msgid ""
"To proceed with an individual finalisation, go to :menuselection:`Payroll --"
"> Reporting --> STP Finalisation`, leave the :guilabel:`EOFY Declaration` "
"checkbox unticked, and manually add employees to be finalised."
msgstr ""
