#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:3
msgid "Accrual plans"
msgstr "休暇累積(付与ルール)"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:5
msgid ""
"Some time off is granted to employees up front, while other kinds of time "
"off are earned through an *accrual plan*, meaning that for every specified "
"amount of time an employee works (hour, day, week, etc), they earn or "
"*accrue* a specified amount of time off."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:10
msgid ""
"If an employee accrues a vacation day for every week they work, they would "
"earn 0.2 vacation days for each hour they worked. At the end of a 40-hour "
"work week, they would earn one full vacation day (8 hours)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:15
msgid "Create an accrual plan"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:17
msgid ""
"To create a new accrual plan, navigate to :menuselection:`Time Off app --> "
"Configuration --> Accrual Plans`. Then, click the :guilabel:`New` button, "
"which reveals a blank *Accrual Plans* form."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:20
msgid ""
"First, enter a :guilabel:`Title` for the accrual plan. If in a multi-company "
"database, a :guilabel:`Company` field appears beneath the :guilabel:`Title` "
"field. Using the drop-down menu, select the company the accrual plan applies "
"to. If left blank, the accrual plan is available for all companies."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:25
msgid "Next, configure the following sections of the form:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:28
#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:131
msgid "Configuration section"
msgstr "設定セクション"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:30
msgid ""
"Configure the following fields in the *Configuration* section of the form:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:32
msgid ""
":guilabel:`When the time is accrued?`: Select when the employee begins to "
"accrue time off, either :guilabel:`At the start of the accrual period` "
"or :guilabel:`At the end of the accrual period`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:34
msgid ""
":guilabel:`It is based on worked time?`: Select how time off accrual is "
"determined. The options are:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:37
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Yes, consider the worked hours, excluding any time off taken "
"during that period.`: Days **not** considered as *worked time* do **not** "
"contribute to the accrual plan in Odoo."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:39
msgid ""
":guilabel:`No, always consider the entire accrual period (whole calendar "
"days).`: Every day is calculated when determining worked time, with no "
"exclusions."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:43
msgid ""
"An employee is granted time off from an accrual plan configured to accrue "
"one day of vacation for every five days worked. The accrual plan is based on "
"the employee's worked time (the :guilabel:`Yes, consider the worked hours, "
"excluding any time off taken during that period.` option is selected), which "
"means they **only** earn vacation time for the five weekdays they work, "
"*not* the entire seven-day week period."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:49
msgid ""
"The employee works a standard 40-hour week. According to the accrual plan, "
"they should earn four vacation days per month."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:52
msgid ""
"The employee takes five days off using a :doc:`time off type "
"<time_off_types>` with the :guilabel:`Counts as` set as "
"an :guilabel:`Absence`. Because the plan grants vacation only for worked "
"time, those five days do not count toward accrual."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:56
msgid ""
"As a result, the employee accrues only three vacation days that month "
"instead of four."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:58
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Do you need a carry-over of the accrued days from one year to "
"another?`: Select when the employee receives previously earned time. The "
"options are:"
msgstr ""
"\\ :guilabel:`前年から今年への繰越が必要ですか`\\ ：従業員が以前に獲得した休"
"暇を受け取るタイミングを選択します。オプションは次のとおりです："

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:61
msgid ""
":guilabel:`At the start of the year`: Select this if the accrual rolls over "
"on January 1 of the upcoming year."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:63
msgid ""
":guilabel:`At the allocation date`: Select this if the accrual rolls over as "
"soon as time is allocated to the employee."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:65
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Custom date`: Select this option if neither of the other two "
"options is applicable. Once selected, set the date using the two drop-down "
"menus, one for the day and one for the month."
msgstr ""
"\\ :guilabel:`カスタム日付`\\ ：他の2つのオプションのいずれも該当しない場合は"
"、このオプションを選択します。選択したら、2つのドロップダウンメニュー（1つは"
"日用、もう1つは月用）を使用して日付を設定します。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:None
msgid "An accrual plan form filled out for a Seniority Plan."
msgstr "勤続年数プランに記入された積立プランフォーム。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:73
msgid "Milestones"
msgstr "マイルストーン"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:75
msgid ""
"Milestones must be created for employees to accrue time off from the accrual "
"plan. Each milestone determines when and how much time off the employee "
"earns."
msgstr ""
"積立プランから休暇を積み立てるには、従業員のマイルストーンを作成する必要があ"
"ります。各マイルストーンは、従業員がいつ、どれだけの休暇を取得するかを決定し"
"ます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:78
msgid ""
"To create a new milestone, click the :guilabel:`Create a milestone` button "
"and a *New Milestone* pop-up window loads. Then fill out the following "
"sections on the form."
msgstr ""
"新しいマイルストーンを作成するには、\\ :guilabel:`マイルストーンを作成`\\ "
"ボタンをクリックすると、*新規マイルストーン*\\ ポップアップウィンドウが読み込"
"まれます。次に、フォームの以下のセクションに記入します。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:82
msgid ""
"Once milestones have been configured, click on a milestone to make edits, "
"click the :icon:`fa-trash-o` :guilabel:`(Delete)` icon to delete it, or "
"click :guilabel:`Add a milestone` to create additional milestones."
msgstr ""
"マイルストーンが設定されたら、マイルストーンをクリックして編集するか、\\ "
":icon:`fa-trash-o`\\ :guilabel:`削除`\\ アイコンをクリックして削除するか、\\ "
":guilabel:`マイルストーンを追加`\\ をクリックして追加のマイルストーンを作成し"
"ます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:None
msgid "An accrual plan form with all the entries filled out."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:90
msgid "Accrual level options section"
msgstr "積立レベルオプションセクション"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:92
msgid "This section determines how much the employee earns, and when."
msgstr "このセクションでは、従業員が獲得する金額とタイミングを決定します。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:94
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Set the employee accrual frequency`: Configure how many hours or "
"days the employee earns in a set period of time."
msgstr ""
"\\ :guilabel:`従業員の積立頻度を設定`\\ ：設定された期間内に従業員が獲得する"
"時間数または日数を設定します。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:97
msgid ""
"The first two fields set *how much* time off the employee earns, while the "
"remaining fields determine *how often* the employee earns the time off."
msgstr ""
"最初の2つのフィールドは、従業員が獲得する休暇の*量*を設定し、残りのフィールド"
"は従業員が休暇を獲得する*頻度*を決定します。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:100
msgid ""
"Enter the numerical amount the employee earns in the first field. The "
"numerical format is `X.XXXX`, so that partial days or hours can be earned. "
"Next, set the middle field to either :guilabel:`Day(s)` "
"or :guilabel:`Hour(s)`."
msgstr ""
"最初のフィールドに、従業員が獲得する数値を入力します。数値形式は `X.XXXX` で"
"あり、部分的な日数または時間数を獲得できます。次に、中央のフィールドを\\ "
":guilabel:`日`\\ または\\ :guilabel:`時間`\\ のいずれかに設定します。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:104
msgid ""
"In the last field, use the drop-down menu to set the frequency the employee "
"earns the time configured in the first two fields. Some options require "
"additional fields to be configured. The default options are:"
msgstr ""
"最後のフィールドでは、ドロップダウンメニューを使用して、最初の2つのフィールド"
"で設定された時間を従業員が獲得する頻度を設定します。一部のオプションでは、追"
"加のフィールドを設定する必要があります。デフォルトのオプションは次のとおりで"
"す："

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:108
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Hourly`: The employee earns the set amount of time for every hour "
"worked. There are no additional fields needed."
msgstr ""
"\\ :guilabel:`毎時`\\ ：従業員は、働いた時間ごとに設定された時間を獲得します"
"。追加のフィールドは必要ありません。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:110
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Daily`: The employee earns the set amount of time for every day "
"worked. There are no additional fields needed."
msgstr ""
"\\ :guilabel:`毎日`\\ ：従業員は、働いた日ごとに設定された時間を獲得します。"
"追加のフィールドは必要ありません。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:112
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Weekly`: The employee earns the set amount of time for every week "
"worked. When selected, use the drop-down menu to select the specific day of "
"the week in the field that appears."
msgstr ""
"\\ :guilabel:`毎週`\\ ：従業員は、働いた週ごとに設定された時間を獲得します。"
"選択すると、ドロップダウンメニューを使用して、表示されるフィールドで曜日を選"
"択します。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:115
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Twice a month`: The employee earns the set amount of time, twice "
"a month, on two specific days. When selected, use the drop-down menus to "
"select the specific days of the month in the two fields that appear."
msgstr ""
"\\ :guilabel:`月2回`\\ ：従業員は、月に2回、2つの特定の日に設定された時間を獲"
"得します。選択すると、ドロップダウンメニューを使用して、表示される2つの"
"フィールドで月の特定の日を選択します。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:118
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Monthly`: The employee earns the set amount of time for every "
"month worked. When selected, use the drop-down menu to select the specific "
"day of the month in the field that appears."
msgstr ""
"\\ :guilabel:`毎月`\\ ：従業員は、働いた月ごとに設定された時間を獲得します。"
"選択すると、ドロップダウンメニューを使用して、表示されるフィールドで月の特定"
"の日を選択します。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:121
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Twice a year`: The employee earns the set amount of time, twice a "
"year, on two specific dates. When selected, use the drop-down menus to "
"select the specific day and month, in the four fields that appear."
msgstr ""
"\\ :guilabel:`年2回`\\ ：従業員は、年に2回、2つの特定の日付に設定された時間を"
"獲得します。選択すると、ドロップダウンメニューを使用して、表示される4つの"
"フィールドで特定の日と月を選択します。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:124
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Yearly`: The employee earns the set amount of time, once a year, "
"on a specific day. When selected, use the drop-down menus to select the "
"specific day and month in the two fields that appear."
msgstr ""
"\\ :guilabel:`毎年`\\ ：従業員は、年に1回、特定の日に設定された時間を獲得しま"
"す。選択すると、ドロップダウンメニューを使用して、表示される2つのフィールドで"
"特定の日と月を選択します。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:127
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Per Hour Worked`: The employee earns the set amount of time for "
"every hour worked. There are no additional fields needed."
msgstr ""
"\\ :guilabel:`時間単位`\\ ：従業員は、労働時間1時間ごとに設定された付与数を獲"
"得します。追加フィールドは必要ありません。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:130
msgid ""
":guilabel:`This milestone will be reached`: This selection determines *when* "
"the employee starts to earn the time off. The options are:"
msgstr ""
"\\ :guilabel:`このマイルストーンに到達する時期`\\ ：この選択により、従業員が"
"休暇を獲得し\\ *始める*\\ 時期が決まります。オプションは次のとおりです："

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:133
msgid ""
":guilabel:`At allocation creation`: The time off starts accruing immediately."
msgstr "\\ :guilabel:`割り当て作成時`\\ ：休暇は即座に付与され始めます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:134
msgid ""
":guilabel:`After (#) (Time) from the start of the allocation.`: Use the "
"first two fields to set the time period the employee achieves the milestone. "
"Enter a number in the first field, then set the middle field to "
"either :guilabel:`Days`, :guilabel:`Months`, or :guilabel:`Years`."
msgstr ""
"\\ :guilabel:`割り当て開始から（#）（時間）後`\\ ：最初の2つのフィールドを使"
"用して、従業員がマイルストーンを達成するまでの期間を設定します。最初の"
"フィールドに数値を入力し、中央のフィールドを\\ :guilabel:`日`\\ 、\\ "
":guilabel:`月`\\ 、または\\ :guilabel:`年`\\ のいずれかに設定します。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:None
msgid "An accrual plan set to give 10 days a year to employees."
msgstr "従業員に年間10日を付与するように設定された付与プラン。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:142
msgid "Carry over options section"
msgstr "繰越オプションセクション"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:144
msgid ""
"This section determines what happens to any unused time off at the end of "
"the year. Configure the following field:"
msgstr ""
"このセクションでは、年度末に未使用の休暇がどうなるかを決定します。次の"
"フィールドを設定します："

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:147
msgid ""
":guilabel:`After a year, unused time off will be:`: Select :guilabel:`Lost` "
"if any unused time off is lost, and does **not** carry over to the following "
"year. Select :guilabel:`Carried over` if time off is rolled over to the next "
"year. When this option is selected, two additional sections appear:"
msgstr ""
"\\ :guilabel:`1年後、未使用の休暇は次のようになります`\\ ：未使用の休暇が失わ"
"れ、翌年に繰り越され\\ **ない**\\ 場合は\\ :guilabel:`失効`\\ を選択します。"
"休暇が翌年に繰り越される場合は\\ :guilabel:`繰り越し`\\ を選択します。この"
"オプションを選択すると、2つの追加セクションが表示されます："

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:152
msgid ""
":guilabel:`How much time can be carried over:`: Select :guilabel:`Unlimited` "
"if *all* time off can be carried over. Select :guilabel:`Up to (#) Day(s)` "
"if there *is* a limit. Enter the total number of days the employee can carry "
"over from one year to the next in the blank field."
msgstr ""
"\\ :guilabel:`繰り越し可能な時間数`\\ ：\\ *すべて*\\ の休暇を繰り越せる場合"
"は\\ :guilabel:`無制限`\\ を選択します。制限が\\ *ある*\\ 場合は\\ "
":guilabel:`最大（#）日`\\ を選択します。空白フィールドに、従業員が1年から次の"
"年に繰り越せる合計日数を入力します。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:155
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Define a carry over validity?`: If there is an expiration date "
"for the carried over time off, enable this option. When enabled, the "
"following appears: :guilabel:`The days carried over will be effective for "
"(#) (Days or Months)`. Enter a number in the first field, then set the "
"second field to either :guilabel:`Days` or :guilabel:`Months`."
msgstr ""
"\\ :guilabel:`繰越有効期限を定義しますか？`\\ ：繰り越された休暇に有効期限が"
"ある場合は、このオプションを有効にします。有効にすると、次のように表示されま"
"す：\\ :guilabel:`繰り越された日数は（#）（日または月）有効です`\\ 。最初の"
"フィールドに数値を入力し、2番目のフィールドを\\ :guilabel:`日`\\ または\\ "
":guilabel:`月`\\ のいずれかに設定します。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:None
msgid "The Carry Over section configured to have unlimited carry over time."
msgstr "無制限の繰越時間を持つように設定された繰越セクション。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:164
msgid "Cap options section"
msgstr "上限オプションセクション"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:166
msgid "This section sets limits on total time off earned."
msgstr "このセクションでは、獲得できる休暇の合計に制限を設定します。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:168
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Define a yearly cap?`: Enable this option to set a limit on the "
"total amount of time that can be accrued every calendar year. When enabled, "
"the following line appears: :guilabel:`Accrual will stop until next carry-"
"over date if accrued time's reach (#) Day(s).` Enter the maximum number of "
"days the employee can earn in the number field."
msgstr ""
"\\ :guilabel:`年間上限を定義しますか？`\\ ：毎年付与される休暇の合計に制限を"
"設定する場合は、このオプションを有効にします。有効にすると、次の行が表示され"
"ます：\\ :guilabel:`付与された時間が（#）日に達すると、次の繰越日まで付与が停"
"止されます`\\ 。従業員が獲得できる最大日数を数値フィールドに入力します。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:172
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Define a balance cap?`: If there is a maximum amount of time the "
"employee can accrue with this plan, enable this option. When enabled, the "
"following line appears: :guilabel:`The plan will be on hold if the balance "
"reach (#) Day(s) of available time.` Enter the maximum number of days the "
"employee can have at any given time in the number field. Any time off beyond "
"this parameter is lost."
msgstr ""
"\\ :guilabel:`残高上限を定義しますか？`\\ ：このプランで従業員が付与できる最"
"大時間数がある場合は、このオプションを有効にします。有効にすると、次の行が表"
"示されます：\\ :guilabel:`残高が（#）日の対応可能時間に達すると、プランは保留"
"になります`\\ 。従業員がいつでも保有できる最大日数を数値フィールドに入力しま"
"す。このパラメータを超える休暇は失われます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:178
msgid ""
"When completed, click :guilabel:`Save` to save the milestone, "
"or :guilabel:`Save & New` to save the milestone and create a new one."
msgstr ""
"完了したら、\\ :guilabel:`保存`\\ をクリックしてマイルストーンを保存するか"
"、\\ :guilabel:`保存&さらに表示`\\ をクリックしてマイルストーンを保存し、新し"
"いマイルストーンを作成します。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:None
msgid "A balance cap of 30 days set in the Cap Options section."
msgstr "上限オプションセクションで30日の残高上限が設定されています。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:185
msgid ""
"This milestone form is configured so the employee earns two weeks (10 days) "
"a year when they are hired, three weeks (15 days) after three years, and a "
"month (20 days) after five years. They start to earn this time yearly, on "
"January 1st."
msgstr ""
"このマイルストーンフォームは、従業員が雇用時に年間2週間（10日）、3年後に3週間"
"（15日）、5年後に1か月（20日）を獲得するように設定されています。この時間は、"
"毎年1月1日から獲得し始めます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:189
msgid ""
"The employee can never accrue more than 30 days in the first three years, 45 "
"days from years 3-5, and 100 days after five years. Anytime they exceed "
"those amounts for the respective years, they will stop accruing more time "
"off."
msgstr ""
"従業員は、最初の3年間は30日以上、3~5年目は45日以上、5年後は100日以上を付与さ"
"れることはありません。それぞれの年数でこれらの金額を超えた場合、休暇の付与は"
"停止されます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:193
msgid ""
"Additionally, they can roll over all their unused time off during the first "
"five years, then they can only rollover 20 days from one year to the next."
msgstr ""
"さらに、最初の5年間は未使用の休暇をすべて繰り越すことができますが、その後は1"
"年から次の年に20日のみ繰り越すことができます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:196
msgid ""
"Note that in year five, the employee can have a yearly cap of 60 days, and a "
"total balance cap of 100 days."
msgstr ""
"5年目には、従業員は年間上限60日、合計残高上限100日を設定できることに注意して"
"ください。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:0
msgid "A milestone form with all the entries filled out."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:3
msgid "Allocations"
msgstr "割当"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:5
msgid ""
"Allocations are amounts of time off given to employees, either granted "
"immediately or earned as the employee works, through an accrual plan."
msgstr ""
"割当は従業員に与えられる休暇時間の量であり、即座に付与されるか、累積計画を通"
"じて従業員が働くことで獲得されます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:8
msgid ""
"Once :doc:`time off type <../time_off/time_off_types>` and :doc:`accrual "
"plan <../time_off/accrual_plans>` have been configured, the next step is to "
"*allocate*, or give, time off to employees."
msgstr ""
"\\ :doc:`休暇タイプ <../time_off/time_off_types>`\\ と\\ :doc:`休暇累積(付与"
"ルール) <../time_off/accrual_plans>`\\ を設定したら、次のステップは従業員に休"
"暇を*割り当てる*ことです。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:12
msgid ""
"The *Allocations* page of the **Time Off** app is **only** visible to users "
"who have either *Time Off Officer* or *Administrator* access rights for the "
"**Time Off** application. For more information on access rights, refer to "
"the :doc:`access rights <../../general/users/access_rights/>` documentation."
msgstr ""
"\\ **休暇**\\ アプリの\\ *割当*\\ ページは、\\ **休暇**\\ アプリケーション"
"の\\ *休暇管理者*\\ または\\ *管理者*\\ のいずれかのアクセス権を持つユーザに"
"のみ表示されます。アクセス権の詳細については、\\ :doc:`アクセス権 <../../"
"general/users/access_rights/>`\\ のドキュメントを参照してください。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:20
msgid "Allocate time off"
msgstr "休暇を付与する"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:22
msgid ""
"To create a new allocation, navigate to :menuselection:`Time Off app --> "
"Management --> Allocations`."
msgstr ""
"新しい割当を作成するには、\\ :menuselection:`休暇アプリ --> 管理 --> 割当`\\ "
"に移動します。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:25
msgid ""
"This presents a list of all current allocations, including their respective "
"statuses."
msgstr "これにより、現在のすべての割当とそれぞれのステータスの一覧が表示されます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:27
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`New` to allocate time off, and a "
"blank :guilabel:`Allocation` form appears."
msgstr ""
"\\ :guilabel:`新規`\\ をクリックして休暇を割り当てると、空白の\\ "
":guilabel:`割当`\\ フォームが表示されます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:29
msgid ""
"After entering a name for the allocation on the first blank field of the "
"form, enter the following information:"
msgstr ""
"フォームの最初の空白フィールドに割当の名前を入力した後、以下の情報を入力しま"
"す:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:32
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Name`: Enter a name for the allocation, typically containing the "
"type of time off, and the period of time it is available (example: `Annual "
"Vacation Time Off - 2025`)."
msgstr ""
"\\ :guilabel:`名前`: 割当の名前を入力します。通常は休暇の種類とそれが利用可能"
"な期間を含めます（例: `年次休暇 - 2025`）。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:34
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Time Off Type`: Using the drop-down menu, select the type of time "
"off that is being allocated to the employees."
msgstr ""
"\\ :guilabel:`休暇タイプ`: ドロップダウンメニューを使用して、従業員に割り当て"
"られる休暇のタイプを選択します。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:36
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Allocation Type`: Select how the allocation is granted. "
"Choose :guilabel:`Regular Allocation` if the time off is given immediately, "
"or :guilabel:`Accrual Allocation` if the time off is earned through "
"an :doc:`accrual plan <../time_off/accrual_plans>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`割当タイプ`\\ :割当の付与方法を選択します。休暇が即座に付与される"
"場合は\\ :guilabel:`通常割当`\\ を、\\ :doc:`休暇累積(付与ルール) <../"
"time_off/accrual_plans>`\\ を通じて休暇が累積される場合は\\ :guilabel:`累積割"
"当`\\ を選択します。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:39
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Accrual Plan`: If :guilabel:`Accrual Allocation` is selected for "
"the :guilabel:`Allocation Type`, the :guilabel:`Accrual Plan` field appears. "
"Using the drop-down menu, select the accrual plan associated with the "
"allocation. An accrual plan is **required** when using "
"the :guilabel:`Accrual Allocation` type."
msgstr ""
"\\ :guilabel:`累積計画`: :guilabel:`割当タイプ`\\ に\\ :guilabel:`累積割当`\\"
" が選択されている場合、\\ :guilabel:`累積計画`\\ フィールドが表示されます。"
"ドロップダウンメニューを使用して、割当に関連付けられた累積計画を選択します"
"。\\ :guilabel:`累積割当`\\ タイプを使用する場合、累積計画は\\ **必須**\\ で"
"す。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:43
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Validity Period/Start Date`: If :guilabel:`Regular Allocation` is "
"selected for the :guilabel:`Allocation Type`, this field is "
"labeled :guilabel:`Validity Period`. If :guilabel:`Accrual Allocation` is "
"selected for the :guilabel:`Allocation Type`, this field is "
"labeled :guilabel:`Start Date`."
msgstr ""
"\\ :guilabel:`有効期間/開始日`: :guilabel:`割当タイプ`\\ に\\ :guilabel:`通常"
"割当`\\ が選択されている場合、このフィールドは\\ :guilabel:`有効期間`\\ とい"
"うラベルになります。\\ :guilabel:`割当タイプ`\\ に\\ :guilabel:`累積割当`\\ "
"が選択されている場合、このフィールドは\\ :guilabel:`開始日`\\ というラベルに"
"なります。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:48
msgid ""
"The current date populates the first date field, by default. To select "
"another date, click on the pre-populated date to reveal a popover calendar "
"window. Navigate to the desired start date for the allocation, and click on "
"the date to select it."
msgstr ""
"デフォルトでは、最初の日付フィールドに現在の日付が入力されます。別の日付を選"
"択するには、事前入力された日付をクリックして"
"ポップオーバーカレンダーウィンドウを表示します。割り当ての開始日に移動し、日"
"付をクリックして選択します。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:52
msgid ""
"If the allocation expires, select the expiration date in the next date "
"field. If the time off does *not* expire, leave the second date field blank."
msgstr ""
"割り当てが期限切れになる場合は、次の日付フィールドで有効期限を選択します。休"
"暇が期限切れに*ならない*場合は、2番目の日付フィールドを空白のままにします。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:55
msgid ""
"If :guilabel:`Accrual Allocation` is selected for the :guilabel:`Allocation "
"Type`, this second field is labeled :guilabel:`Run until`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`割り当てタイプ`に:guilabel:`累積割当`が選択されている場合、この2番"
"目のフィールドには:guilabel:`実行期限`というラベルが付けられます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:57
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Allocation`: Enter the amount of time that is being allocated to "
"the employees. This field displays the time in either :guilabel:`Hours` "
"or :guilabel:`Days`, depending on how the selected  :doc:`Time Off Type <../"
"time_off/time_off_types>` is configured."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`付与数`：従業員に付与される時間数を入力します。このフィールドは、"
"選択された:doc:`休暇タイプ <../time_off/time_off_types>`の設定方法に応じて"
"、:guilabel:`時間`または:guilabel:`日数`で時間を表示します。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:60
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Employee`: Using the drop-down menu, select the employee being "
"allocated the time off."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`従業員`: ドロップダウンメニューを使用して、休暇を割り当てる従業員"
"を選択します。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:61
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Add a reason...`: If any description or note is necessary to "
"explain the time off allocation, enter it in this field at the bottom of the "
"form."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`理由を追加...`: 休暇の割り当てを説明するための説明またはメモが必要"
"な場合は、フォームの下部にあるこのフィールドに入力します。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:None
msgid ""
"A new allocation form with all the fields filled out for the annual two week "
"vacation\n"
"granted to all employees."
msgstr ""
"すべての従業員に付与される年次2週間の休暇のためにすべてのフィールドが入力され"
"た新しい割り当てフォーム。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:69
msgid "Accrual start date behavior"
msgstr "累積開始日の動作"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:71
msgid ""
"If the :guilabel:`Start Date` is in the middle of an accrual period, Odoo "
"adjusts it to the start or end of that period based on the *Accrued Gain "
"Time* entered on the :doc:`accrual plan <../time_off/accrual_plans>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`開始日`\\ が累積期間の途中にある場合、Odooは\\ :doc:`休暇累積(付与"
"ルール) <../time_off/accrual_plans>`\\ に入力された*累積取得時間*に基づいて、"
"その期間の開始または終了に調整します。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:76
msgid ""
"*At the start of the accrual period*: A :guilabel:`Start Date` of `06/16/25` "
"applies from `06/01/25`"
msgstr ""
"*累積期間の開始時*:\\ :guilabel:`開始日`\\ が`06/16/25`の場合、`06/01/25`から"
"適用されます"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:78
msgid ""
"*At the end of the accrual period*: A :guilabel:`Start Date` of `06/18/25` "
"applies from `07/01/25`"
msgstr ""
"*累積期間の終了時*:\\ :guilabel:`開始日`\\ が`06/18/25`の場合、`07/01/25`から"
"適用されます"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:81
msgid ""
"Automatic adjustments on the start date to either the begining or end of an "
"accural period ensures accruals align with the defined period boundaries, "
"rather than the exact date entered."
msgstr ""
"開始日の累積期間の開始または終了への自動調整により、入力された正確な日付では"
"なく、定義された期間境界に累積が確実に整合されます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:85
msgid "Multiple requests"
msgstr "複数の申請"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:87
msgid ""
"When allocating time off, it is common to allocate time to several employees "
"at once. This is done using the :guilabel:`Multiple Requests` feature."
msgstr ""
"休暇を割り当てる際、複数の従業員に一度に時間を割り当てることが一般的です。こ"
"れは、:guilabel:`複数の申請`機能を使用して行われます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:90
msgid ""
"To allocate time to multiple employees in a single allocation, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Time Off app --> Management --> Allocations`. Then, click "
"the :icon:`fa-gear` :guilabel:`(Actions)` icon in the upper-left corner, "
"then click :icon:`fa-users` :guilabel:`Multiple Requests`. This reveals "
"a :guilabel:`Multiple Requests` pop-up window."
msgstr ""
"1回の割り当てで複数の従業員に時間を割り当てるには、:menuselection:`休暇"
"アプリ --> 管理 --> 割り当て`に移動します。次に、左上隅の:icon:`fa-gear`\\ "
":guilabel:`アクション`アイコンをクリックし、:icon:`fa-users`\\ :guilabel:`複"
"数の申請`をクリックします。これにより、:guilabel:`複数の申"
"請`ポップアップウィンドウが表示されます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:95
msgid ""
"This form is identical to the :ref:`Allocation form <time_off/allocation-"
"form>`, with an additional :guilabel:`Mode` field. The :guilabel:`Mode` "
"field determines how multiple employees are selected."
msgstr ""
"このフォームは、追加の:guilabel:`モード`フィールドを除いて、:ref:`割り当て"
"フォーム <time_off/allocation-form>`と同じです。:guilabel:`モード`フィールド"
"は、複数の従業員の選択方法を決定します。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:98
msgid ""
"Using the drop-down menu, select a :guilabel:`Mode` from one of the "
"following options:"
msgstr ""
"ドロップダウンメニューを使用して、次のオプションから:guilabel:`モード`を選択"
"します:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:100
msgid ""
":guilabel:`By Employee`: This option allows for the selection of multiple "
"individual employees that are unrelated in terms of department, company, or "
"tags. Selecting this reveals an :guilabel:`Employees` field. Select the "
"employees to receive the allocation in the :guilabel:`Employees` field. "
"There is no limit to the amount of employees that can be selected."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`従業員別`: このオプションを使用すると、部門、会社、またはタグに関"
"連しない複数の個別従業員を選択できます。これを選択すると、:guilabel:`従業"
"員`フィールドが表示されます。:guilabel:`従業員`フィールドで、割り当てを受け取"
"る従業員を選択します。選択できる従業員の数に制限はありません。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:104
msgid ""
":guilabel:`By Company`: This option allows for the selection of all "
"employees within a specific company. Selecting this reveals "
"a :guilabel:`Company` field. Select the :guilabel:`Company` to assign the "
"allocation to. Only one company can be assigned in the :guilabel:`Company` "
"field. When a company is selected, *all* employees within the company "
"receive the allocation."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`会社別`: このオプションを使用すると、特定の会社内のすべての従業員"
"を選択できます。これを選択すると、:guilabel:`会社`フィールドが表示されます。"
"割り当てを割り当てる:guilabel:`会社`を選択します。:guilabel:`会社`フィールド"
"では、1つの会社のみを割り当てることができます。会社が選択されると、会社内"
"の*すべての*従業員が割り当てを受け取ります。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:108
msgid ""
":guilabel:`By Department`: This option allows for the selection of all "
"employees within a specific department. Selecting this reveals "
"a :guilabel:`Department` field. Select the :guilabel:`Department` to assign "
"the allocation to. Only one department can be assigned in "
"the :guilabel:`Department` field. When a department is selected, *all* "
"employees within the department receive the allocation."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`部門別`: このオプションを使用すると、特定の部門内のすべての従業員"
"を選択できます。これを選択すると、:guilabel:`部門`フィールドが表示されます。"
"割り当てを割り当てる:guilabel:`部門`を選択します。:guilabel:`部門`フィールド"
"では、1つの部門のみを割り当てることができます。部門が選択されると、部門内"
"の*すべての*従業員が割り当てを受け取ります。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:113
msgid ""
":guilabel:`By Employee Tag`: This option allows for the selection of all "
"employees with a specific tag. Selecting this reveals an :guilabel:`Employee "
"Tag` field. Select the desired :guilabel:`Employee Tag` to select all "
"employees with that tag. Only one tag can be assigned in "
"the :guilabel:`Employee Tag` field. When a tag is selected, *all* employees "
"with that tag receive the allocation."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`従業員タグ別`: このオプションを使用すると、特定のタグを持つすべて"
"の従業員を選択できます。これを選択すると、:guilabel:`従業員タグ`フィールドが"
"表示されます。そのタグを持つすべての従業員を選択するには、目的の:guilabel:`従"
"業員タグ`を選択します。:guilabel:`従業員タグ`フィールドでは、1つのタグのみを"
"割り当てることができます。タグが選択されると、そのタグを持つ*すべての*従業員"
"が割り当てを受け取ります。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:119
msgid ""
"Next, select the :guilabel:`Time Off Type` using the drop-down menu. Once "
"a :guilabel:`Time Off Type` is selected, the placeholder name, 'Allocation "
"Request', changes to the name of the selected :guilabel:`Time Off Type`, "
"including the amount of days. Change the name of the allocation, if desired."
msgstr ""
"次に、ドロップダウンメニューを使用して:guilabel:`休暇タイプ`を選択します"
"。:guilabel:`休暇タイプ`が選択されると、プレースホルダー名「割り当て申請」が"
"、選択された:guilabel:`休暇タイプ`の名前(日数を含む)に変更されます。必要に応"
"じて、割り当ての名前を変更します。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:124
msgid ""
"Fill out the remainder of the :ref:`Multiple Requests form <time_off/"
"allocation-form>`, then click :guilabel:`Create Allocations` when done."
msgstr ""
"残りの:ref:`複数申請フォーム <time_off/allocation-form>`\\ に入力し、完了した"
"ら\\ :guilabel:`付与作成`\\ をクリックします。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:128
msgid ""
"A company hosts an annual picnic, including a raffle. There are five raffle "
"prizes for a free vacation day, which must be redeemed by the end of the "
"year. The winners of this raffle all have the tag `Raffle Winner - 2025 "
"Employee Picnic Prize` added to their employee profiles."
msgstr ""
"ある会社が年次ピクニックを開催し、抽選会を行います。無料の休暇日が当たる抽選"
"賞品が5つあり、年末までに引き換える必要があります。この抽選の当選者全員の従業"
"員プロフィールに「Raffle Winner - 2025 Employee Picnic Prize」タグが追加され"
"ます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:132
msgid ""
"The time off officer creates multiple allocations, and configures "
"the :ref:`Multiple Requests form <time_off/allocation-form>` as follows:"
msgstr ""
"休暇担当者は複数の付与を作成し、:ref:`複数申請フォーム <time_off/allocation-"
"form>`\\ を次のように設定します："

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:135
msgid ""
"The name for the allocation is :guilabel:`Vacation Day - Raffle Prize - 2025 "
"Picnic`. The :guilabel:`Mode` is set to :guilabel:`By Employee Tag`, and "
"the :guilabel:`Tag` identified is :guilabel:`Raffle Winner - 2025 Employee "
"Picnic Prize`."
msgstr ""
"付与の名前は\\ :guilabel:`Vacation Day - Raffle Prize - 2025 Picnic`\\ です"
"。:guilabel:`モード`\\ は\\ :guilabel:`従業員タグ別`\\ に設定され"
"、:guilabel:`タグ`\\ は\\ :guilabel:`Raffle Winner - 2025 Employee Picnic "
"Prize`\\ として識別されます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:139
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Time Off Type` is set to :guilabel:`Vacation Time Off`, with "
"the :guilabel:`Allocation Type` set to :guilabel:`Regular Allocaiton`, since "
"the time off is given up front, and is not *earned*."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`休暇タイプ`\\ は\\ :guilabel:`Vacation Time Off`\\ に設定され"
"、:guilabel:`付与タイプ`\\ は\\ :guilabel:`通常付与`\\ に設定されます。これは"
"休暇が前払いで付与され、*取得*するものではないためです。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:143
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Validity Period` is set to :guilabel:`07/18/2025` :icon:`oi-"
"arrow-right` :guilabel:`12/31/2025`, since the compnay picnic was that day, "
"and the earned vacation day expires at the end of the year."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`有効期間`\\ は\\ :guilabel:`07/18/2025`:icon:`oi-arrow-"
"right`:guilabel:`12/31/2025`\\ に設定されます。これは会社のピクニックがその日"
"に開催され、取得した休暇日が年末に失効するためです。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:147
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Allocation` is set to :guilabel:`1.00 Days`, and `A bonus "
"vacation day won at the annual Company Picnic.` appears in the details at "
"the bottom."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`付与数`\\ は\\ :guilabel:`1.00 Days`\\ に設定され、下部の詳細に「"
"A bonus vacation day won at the annual Company Picnic.」と表示されます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:0
msgid ""
"An allocation request form filled out for a bonus vacation day for raffle "
"winners."
msgstr "抽選当選者のボーナス休暇日の付与申請フォームが入力されています。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:156
msgid "Request allocation"
msgstr "付与申請"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:158
msgid ""
"If an employee has used all their time off, or will run out of time off, "
"they can request an allocation for additional time. Allocations can be "
"requested in one of two ways, either from the :ref:`Dashboard <time_off/"
"dashboard>` or the :ref:`My Allocations <time_off/my-allocations>` view."
msgstr ""
"従業員が休暇をすべて使用した場合、または休暇が不足する場合は、追加の休暇の付"
"与を申請できます。付与は、:ref:`ダッシュュボード <time_off/dashboard>`\\ また"
"は\\ :ref:`個人の付与 <time_off/my-allocations>`\\ ビューの2つの方法で申請で"
"きます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:162
msgid ""
"To create a new allocation request, click either the :guilabel:`New "
"Allocation Request` button on the main **Time Off** dashboard, or "
"the :guilabel:`New` button in the :guilabel:`My Allocations` list view. Both "
"buttons open a new allocation request form."
msgstr ""
"新しい付与申請を作成するには、**休暇**ダッシュボードのメイン画面の\\ "
":guilabel:`新規付与申請`\\ ボタン、または\\ :guilabel:`個人の付与`\\ "
"リストビューの\\ :guilabel:`新規`\\ ボタンをクリックします。どちらのボタンも"
"新しい付与申請フォームを開きます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:167
msgid ""
"Both options open a new allocation request form, but when requested from "
"the :guilabel:`Dashboard`, the form appears in a pop-up window, and the "
"*Validity Period* field does **not** appear."
msgstr ""
"どちらのオプションも新しい付与申請フォームを開きますが"
"、:guilabel:`ダッシュュボード`\\ から申請する場合は、フォームが"
"ポップアップウィンドウで表示され、*有効期間*フィールドは**表示されません**。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:171
msgid ""
"When requested from the :guilabel:`My Allocations` list view, the screen "
"navigates to a new allocation request page, instead of presenting a pop-up "
"window."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`個人の付与`\\ リストビューから申請する場合、ポップアップウィンドウ"
"ではなく、新しい付与申請ページに画面が遷移します。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:174
msgid "Enter the following information on the new allocation request form:"
msgstr "新しい付与申請フォームに次の情報を入力します："

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:176
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Time Off Type`: Using the drop-down menu, select the type of time "
"off being requested for the allocation. After a selection is made, the title "
"updates with the time off type."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`休暇タイプ`：ドロップダウンメニューを使用して、付与を申請する休暇"
"のタイプを選択します。選択すると、タイトルが休暇タイプで更新されます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:178
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Validity Period`: By default, the current date populates this "
"field, and it is **not** able to be modified. This field **only** appears "
"when requesting an allocation from the :guilabel:`My Allocations` view "
"(:menuselection:`Time Off --> My Time --> My Allocations`)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`有効期間`：デフォルトでは、このフィールドに現在の日付が入力され、"
"変更は**できません**。このフィールドは、:guilabel:`個人の付与`\\ ビュー"
"（:menuselection:`休暇 --> 個人の休暇 --> 個人の付与`）から付与を申請する場合"
"に**のみ**表示されます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:181
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Allocation`: Enter the amount of time being requested in this "
"field. The format is presented in either :guilabel:`Days` "
"or :guilabel:`Hours`, depending on how the :guilabel:`Time Off Type` is "
"configured. Once this field is populated, the name of the allocation request "
"is updated to include the amount of time being requested."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`付与数`：このフィールドに申請する時間を入力します。形式は"
"、:guilabel:`休暇タイプ`\\ の設定に応じて、:guilabel:`日`\\ または\\ "
":guilabel:`時間`\\ で表示されます。このフィールドに入力すると、付与申請の名前"
"が更新され、申請する時間が含まれます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:185
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Add a reason...`: Enter a description for the allocation request "
"in this field. This should include any details that approvers may need to "
"approve the request."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`理由を追加...`：このフィールドに付与申請の説明を入力します。これに"
"は、承認者が申請を承認するために必要な詳細を含める必要があります。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:188
msgid ""
"If the request was created from the :guilabel:`Dashboard`, click "
"the :guilabel:`Save & Close` button on the :guilabel:`New Allocation` pop-up "
"window to save the information and submit the request."
msgstr ""
"申請が\\ :guilabel:`ダッシュュボード`\\ から作成された場合は、:guilabel:`新規"
"付与`\\ ポップアップウィンドウの\\ :guilabel:`保存して閉じる`\\ ボタンを"
"クリックして、情報を保存し、申請を送信します。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:191
msgid ""
"If the form was completed from the :guilabel:`My Allocations` list view, the "
"information is automatically saved as it is entered."
msgstr ""
"フォームが\\ :guilabel:`個人の付与`\\ リストビューから入力された場合、情報は"
"入力時に自動的に保存されます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:None
msgid ""
"An allocation request form filled out for an employee requesting an "
"additional week of\n"
"sick time."
msgstr "従業員が追加の1週間の病気休暇を申請する配分申請フォームの記入例。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/management.rst:3
msgid "Management"
msgstr "マネジメント"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/management.rst:7
msgid ""
"Time off and allocation requests undergo an approval process before being "
"granted. Requests either need one or two approvals, if any, depending on how "
"the specific type of time off is configured. All these configurations can be "
"found under the *Management* section of the **Time Off** application."
msgstr ""
"休暇および配分の申請は、承認される前に承認プロセスを経ます。申請には、特定の"
"休暇タイプの設定に応じて、1つまたは2つの承認が必要です（承認が必要な場合）。"
"これらの設定はすべて、**休暇**アプリケーションの*管理*セクションで確認できま"
"す。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/management.rst:11
msgid ""
"Only users who can :ref:`approve allocation and time off requests <employees/"
"work-info-tab>` see the :guilabel:`Management` section in the **Time Off** "
"application."
msgstr ""
"\\ :ref:`配分と休暇申請を承認 <employees/work-info-tab>`\\ できるユーザーのみ"
"が、**休暇**アプリケーションの\\ :guilabel:`管理`\\ セクションを表示できます"
"。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/management.rst:17
msgid "Manage time off"
msgstr "休暇を管理"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/management.rst:19
msgid ""
"To view time off requests that need approval, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Time Off app --> Management --> Time Off`. Doing so "
"reveals the :guilabel:`All Time Off` page."
msgstr ""
"承認が必要な休暇申請を表示するには、\\ :menuselection:`休暇アプリ --> 管"
"理 --> 休暇`\\ に移動します。これにより、\\ :guilabel:`すべての休暇`\\ ページ"
"が表示されます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/management.rst:22
msgid ""
"The only time off requests that are visible on this page belong to employees "
"the user either has :guilabel:`Time Off Officer` "
"or :guilabel:`Administrator` access rights for in the **Time Off** "
"application."
msgstr ""
"このページに表示される休暇申請は、**休暇**アプリケーションでユーザーが\\ "
":guilabel:`休暇担当者`\\ または\\ :guilabel:`管理者`\\ のアクセス権を持つ従業"
"員のものだけです。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/management.rst:26
msgid ""
"The default filter on the :guilabel:`All Time Off` page is :icon:`fa-"
"filter` :guilabel:`Waiting For Me`. This filter only presents time off "
"requests that need to be approved for current employees on the user's team, "
"with a status of either :guilabel:`To Approve` or :guilabel:`Second "
"Approval`."
msgstr ""
"\\ :guilabel:`すべての休暇`\\ ページのデフォルトフィルターは\\ :icon:`fa-"
"filter`\\ :guilabel:`自分が承認待ち`\\ です。このフィルターは、ユーザーの"
"チームの現在の従業員について、ステータスが\\ :guilabel:`承認待ち`\\ または\\ "
":guilabel:`2次承認`\\ である休暇申請のみを表示します。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/management.rst:30
msgid ""
"On the left side of the :guilabel:`All Time Off` page, there are various "
"grouping options that can be used to narrow down the presented time off "
"requests, located beneath the :guilabel:`Status` and :guilabel:`Department` "
"headings."
msgstr ""
"\\ :guilabel:`すべての休暇`\\ ページの左側には、表示される休暇申請を絞り込む"
"ために使用できるさまざまなグループ化オプションがあり、\\ "
":guilabel:`ステータス`\\ および\\ :guilabel:`部門`\\ の見出しの下に配置されて"
"います。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/management.rst:34
msgid ""
"Since only time off requests that need to be approved are shown, the "
"only :guilabel:`Status` options are :guilabel:`All`, :guilabel:`To Approve`, "
"and :guilabel:`Second Approval`."
msgstr ""
"承認が必要な休暇申請のみが表示されるため、\\ :guilabel:`ステータス`\\ の"
"オプションは\\ :guilabel:`すべて`\\ 、\\ :guilabel:`承認待ち`\\ 、および\\ "
":guilabel:`2次承認`\\ のみです。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/management.rst:37
msgid ""
"The various departments the user is a member of, and manages employees "
"under, also appear on the left side of the page, "
"under :guilabel:`Departments`."
msgstr ""
"ユーザーがメンバーである、および従業員を管理しているさまざまな部門も、ページ"
"の左側の\\ :guilabel:`部門`\\ の下に表示されます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/management.rst:41
msgid ""
"If no requests fall under one of the status options or departments, that "
"status or department is **not** visible on the left-side menu."
msgstr ""
"ステータスオプションまたは部門のいずれかに該当する申請がない場合、その"
"ステータスまたは部門は左側のメニューに表示**されません**。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/management.rst:44
msgid ""
"To only display time off requests for specific departments, click on "
"the :guilabel:`Department` on the left-hand side of the page. Only requests "
"within the selected department are then presented."
msgstr ""
"特定の部門の休暇申請のみを表示するには、ページの左側にある\\ :guilabel:`部"
"門`\\ をクリックします。選択した部門内の申請のみが表示されます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/management.rst:47
msgid ""
"The status column displays the status of each request, with the status "
"highlighted in a specific color."
msgstr ""
"ステータス列には各申請のステータスが表示され、ステータスは特定の色で強調表示"
"されます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/management.rst:50
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`To Approve` and :guilabel:`Second Approval` requests are "
"highlighted in yellow, and are the only ones that appear in the list by "
"default."
msgstr ""
"\\ :guilabel:`承認待ち`\\ および\\ :guilabel:`2次承認`\\ の申請は黄色で強調表"
"示され、デフォルトでリストに表示されるのはこれらのみです。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/management.rst:53
msgid ""
"If the :icon:`fa-filter` :guilabel:`Waiting For Me` filter is removed, all "
"statuses appear."
msgstr ""
"\\ :icon:`fa-filter`\\ :guilabel:`自分が承認待ち`\\ フィルターを削除すると、"
"すべてのステータスが表示されます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/management.rst:55
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Approved` requests are highlighted in green, :guilabel:`To "
"Submit` (drafts) requests are highlighted in blue, and "
"the :guilabel:`Refused` requests are highlighted in gray."
msgstr ""
"\\ :guilabel:`承認済み`\\ の申請は緑色で強調表示され、\\ :guilabel:`提出待"
"ち`\\ （下書き）の申請は青色で強調表示され、\\ :guilabel:`却下`\\ された申請"
"は灰色で強調表示されます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/management.rst:58
msgid ""
"To approve a time off request, click the :icon:`fa-thumbs-"
"up` :guilabel:`Approve` button at the end of the line."
msgstr ""
"休暇申請を承認するには、行の最後にある\\ :icon:`fa-thumbs-up`\\ :guilabel:`承"
"認`\\ ボタンをクリックします。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/management.rst:61
msgid ""
"To validate a time off request that has already been approved, and is "
"waiting on a second approval, click the :icon:`fa-"
"check` :guilabel:`Validate` button at the end of the line."
msgstr ""
"すでに承認されており、2次承認を待機している休暇申請を最終確定するには、行の最"
"後にある\\ :icon:`fa-check`\\ :guilabel:`確認`\\ ボタンをクリックします。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/management.rst:64
msgid ""
"To refuse a request, click the :icon:`fa-times` :guilabel:`Refuse` button at "
"the far end of the line."
msgstr ""
"申請を却下するには、行の最後にある\\ :icon:`fa-times`\\ :guilabel:`却下`\\ "
"ボタンをクリックします。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/management.rst:None
msgid ""
"Time off requests with the filter, groupings, and status sections "
"highlighted."
msgstr "フィルター、グループ化、およびステータスセクションが強調表示された休暇申請。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/management.rst:70
msgid ""
"For more details, click anywhere on the time off request line (except for "
"the :icon:`fa-thumbs-up` :guilabel:`Approve`, :icon:`fa-"
"check` :guilabel:`Validate` icon, and :icon:`fa-times` :guilabel:`Refuse` "
"buttons). Doing so loads that specific time off request form. Depending on "
"the rights of the user, changes can be made."
msgstr ""
"詳細を確認するには、休暇申請行の任意の場所（\\ :icon:`fa-thumbs-up`\\ "
":guilabel:`確認`、:icon:`fa-check`\\ :guilabel:`最終確定`\\ アイコン、およ"
"び\\ :icon:`fa-times`\\ :guilabel:`却下`\\ ボタンを除く）をクリックします。こ"
"れにより、その特定の休暇申請フォームが読み込まれます。ユーザーの権限に応じて"
"、変更を加えることができます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/management.rst:75
msgid ""
"To modify the request, make any desired changes to the form. All changes are "
"automatically saved."
msgstr ""
"申請を変更するには、フォームに必要な変更を加えます。すべての変更は自動的に保"
"存されます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/management.rst:77
msgid ""
"It is also possible to approve, validate, or refuse the request from this "
"form. Click the :guilabel:`Approve` button to approve, "
"the :guilabel:`Validate` button to validate, or the :guilabel:`Refuse` "
"button to refuse the request."
msgstr ""
"このフォームから申請を承認、最終確定、または却下することもできます。承認する"
"には\\ :guilabel:`確認`\\ ボタンをクリックし、最終確定するには\\ "
":guilabel:`最終確定`\\ ボタンをクリックし、申請を却下するには\\ :guilabel:`却"
"下`\\ ボタンをクリックします。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/management.rst:84
msgid "Manage allocations"
msgstr "割り当てを管理"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/management.rst:86
msgid ""
"To view allocations that need approval, navigate to :menuselection:`Time Off "
"app --> Management --> Allocations`. Doing so reveals "
"the :guilabel:`Allocations` page."
msgstr ""
"承認が必要な割り当てを表示するには、:menuselection:`休暇アプリ --> 管理 --> "
"割り当て`\\ に移動します。これにより、:guilabel:`割り当て`\\ ページが表示され"
"ます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/management.rst:89
msgid ""
"The user is only presented with allocations for employees they have "
"either :guilabel:`Time Off Officer` or :guilabel:`Administrator` access "
"rights for in the **Time Off** application."
msgstr ""
"ユーザーには、**休暇**アプリケーションで\\ :guilabel:`休暇担当者`\\ または\\ "
":guilabel:`管理者`\\ のアクセス権を持つ従業員の割り当てのみが表示されます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/management.rst:92
msgid ""
"The default filters configured on the :guilabel:`Allocations` page "
"are :guilabel:`First Approval` and :guilabel:`My Team`. These default "
"filters only present employees that the user manages and are awaiting their "
"first approval. Approved and refused allocation requests are not shown."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`割り当て`\\ ページで設定されているデフォルトのフィルターは"
"、:guilabel:`初回承認`\\ と\\ :guilabel:`自分のチーム`\\ です。これらの"
"デフォルトフィルターは、ユーザーが管理する従業員で、初回承認待ちの従業員のみ"
"を表示します。承認済みおよび却下された割り当て申請は表示されません。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/management.rst:96
msgid ""
"The left side of the :guilabel:`Allocations` page has various grouping "
"options to narrow down the presented allocation requests."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`割り当て`\\ ページの左側には、表示される割り当て申請を絞り込むため"
"のさまざまなグループ化オプションがあります。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/management.rst:99
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Status` options are: :guilabel:`All`, :guilabel:`To "
"Approve`, :guilabel:`Refused`, and :guilabel:`Approved`. Click on a "
"specific :guilabel:`Status` to view only requests with that specific status."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`ステータス`\\ のオプションは、:guilabel:`すべて`、:guilabel:`承認"
"待ち`、:guilabel:`却下済み`、および\\ :guilabel:`承認済み`\\ です。特定の\\ "
":guilabel:`ステータス`\\ をクリックすると、その特定のステータスの申請のみが表"
"示されます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/management.rst:103
msgid ""
"To view all allocation requests, regardless of status, click :guilabel:`All` "
"under the :guilabel:`Status` heading."
msgstr ""
"ステータスに関係なくすべての割り当て申請を表示するには"
"、:guilabel:`ステータス`\\ 見出しの下にある\\ :guilabel:`すべて`\\ をクリック"
"します。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/management.rst:106
msgid ""
"It is also possible to display allocation requests by department. Click on "
"the desired :guilabel:`Department` on the left side of "
"the :guilabel:`Allocations` page, to only present allocations for that "
"specific department."
msgstr ""
"部門別に割り当て申請を表示することもできます。:guilabel:`割り当て`\\ ページの"
"左側にある目的の\\ :guilabel:`部門`\\ をクリックすると、その特定の部門の割り"
"当てのみが表示されます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/management.rst:111
msgid ""
"The groupings on the left side **only** present allocation requests that "
"fall under the default filters of :guilabel:`My Team` and :guilabel:`Active "
"Employee`, if those default filters are not removed from "
"the :guilabel:`Search...` bar. Only the statuses for allocation requests "
"that fall under those filters are presented on the left side."
msgstr ""
"左側のグループ化は、:guilabel:`検索...`\\ バーからこれらの"
"デフォルトフィルターが削除されていない場合、:guilabel:`自分のチーム`\\ と\\ "
":guilabel:`稼働中の従業員`\\ のデフォルトフィルターに該当する割り当て申請**の"
"み**を表示します。これらのフィルターに該当する割り当て申請のステータスのみが"
"左側に表示されます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/management.rst:116
msgid ""
"For example, if there are no requests with a status of :guilabel:`To "
"Submit`, that status option does not appear in the left-hand side of "
"the :guilabel:`Allocations` page."
msgstr ""
"たとえば、:guilabel:`提出待ち`\\ のステータスの申請がない場合、その"
"ステータスオプションは\\ :guilabel:`割り当て`\\ ページの左側に表示されません"
"。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/management.rst:119
msgid ""
"All departments for the user's employees appear in the list. If there are no "
"allocation requests that fall under that department matching the "
"preconfigured filters, the list is blank."
msgstr ""
"ユーザーの従業員のすべての部門がリストに表示されます。事前設定された"
"フィルターに一致するその部門に該当する割り当て申請がない場合、リストは空白に"
"なります。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/management.rst:122
msgid ""
"It is always possible to remove any of the preconfigured filters, by "
"clicking the :icon:`fa-times` :guilabel:`(remove)` icon on the specific "
"filter to remove it."
msgstr ""
"事前設定されたフィルターを削除するには、削除する特定のフィルターの\\ "
":icon:`fa-times`\\ :guilabel:`（削除）`\\ アイコンをクリックすることで、いつ"
"でも削除できます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/management.rst:125
msgid ""
"The status column displays the status of each request, with the status "
"highlighted in a specific color. The :guilabel:`To Approve` requests are "
"highlighted in yellow, and if the default :guilabel:`First Approval` filter "
"is removed, the :guilabel:`Approved` requests are highlighted in green, and "
"the :guilabel:`Refused` requests are highlighted in gray."
msgstr ""
"ステータス列には各申請のステータスが表示され、ステータスは特定の色で強調表示"
"されます。:guilabel:`承認待ち`\\ の申請は黄色で強調表示され、デフォルトの\\ "
":guilabel:`初回承認`\\ フィルターが削除されると、:guilabel:`承認済み`\\ の申"
"請は緑色で強調表示され、:guilabel:`却下済み`\\ の申請は灰色で強調表示されます"
"。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/management.rst:130
msgid ""
"To approve an allocation request, click the :icon:`fa-thumbs-"
"up` :guilabel:`Approve` button at the end of the line. To refuse a request, "
"click the :icon:`fa-times` :guilabel:`Refuse` button."
msgstr ""
"割り当て申請を承認するには、行の末尾にある\\ :icon:`fa-thumbs-up`\\ "
":guilabel:`確認`\\ ボタンをクリックします。申請を却下するには、:icon:`fa-"
"times`\\ :guilabel:`却下`\\ ボタンをクリックします。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/management.rst:None
msgid ""
"Allocations with the filter, groupings, and status sections highlighted."
msgstr "フィルター、グループ化、ステータスのセクションが強調表示された割り当て。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/management.rst:136
msgid ""
"If more details are needed, click anywhere on the allocation request line "
"(except for the :icon:`fa-thumbs-up` :guilabel:`Approve` or :icon:`fa-"
"times` :guilabel:`Refuse` buttons) to view the specific request in detail, "
"via the allocation request form."
msgstr ""
"詳細が必要な場合は、割り当て申請行の任意の場所（\\ :icon:`fa-thumbs-up`\\ "
":guilabel:`確認`\\ または\\ :icon:`fa-times`\\ :guilabel:`却下`\\ ボタンを除"
"く）をクリックして、割り当て申請フォームを介して特定の申請の詳細を表示します"
"。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/management.rst:140
msgid ""
"Depending on the rights of the user, changes can be made to the allocation "
"request form that appears. To modify the request, make any desired changes "
"to the form. All changes are automatically saved."
msgstr ""
"ユーザーの権限に応じて、表示される割り当て申請フォームに変更を加えることがで"
"きます。申請を変更するには、フォームに必要な変更を加えます。すべての変更は自"
"動的に保存されます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/management.rst:144
msgid ""
"It is also possible to approve or refuse the request from this form. Click "
"the :guilabel:`Approve` button to approve, or the :guilabel:`Refuse` button "
"to refuse the request."
msgstr ""
"このフォームから申請を承認または却下することも可能です。承認する場合は\\ "
":guilabel:`承認`\\ ボタンをクリックし、申請を却下する場合は\\ :guilabel:`却"
"下`\\ ボタンをクリックします。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/my_time.rst:3
msgid "My time"
msgstr "自分の時間"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/my_time.rst:5
msgid ""
"The *My Time* menu of the **Time Off** app houses all the various time off "
"information for the signed-in user."
msgstr ""
"**休暇**アプリの*自分の時間*メニューには、ログインしているユーザのさまざまな"
"休暇情報がすべて格納されています。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/my_time.rst:8
msgid ""
"This includes the main **Time Off** :ref:`dashboard <time_off/dashboard>`, "
"which displays an overview of the various time off balances, as well "
"as :ref:`time-off requests <time_off/my-time-off>` and :ref:`allocations "
"<time_off/my-allocations>`."
msgstr ""
"これには、メインの**休暇**\\ :ref:`ダッシュボード <time_off/dashboard>`\\ が"
"含まれており、さまざまな休暇残高の概要が表示されるほか、\\ :ref:`休暇申請 "
"<time_off/my-time-off>`\\ および\\ :ref:`割り当て <time_off/my-allocations>"
"`\\ も表示されます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/my_time.rst:15
msgid "Dashboard"
msgstr "ダッシュボード"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/my_time.rst:17
msgid ""
"All users have access to the **Time Off** :guilabel:`Dashboard`, which is "
"the first page that appears when the **Time Off** app is opened. "
"The :guilabel:`Dashboard` can also be accessed at any point in the "
"application, by navigating to :menuselection:`Time Off app --> My Time --> "
"Dashboard`."
msgstr ""
"すべてのユーザが**休暇**\\ :guilabel:`ダッシュボード`\\ にアクセスでき、これ"
"は**休暇**アプリを開いたときに最初に表示されるページです。\\ "
":guilabel:`ダッシュボード`\\ は、アプリケーション内のどの時点でも\\ "
":menuselection:`休暇アプリ --> 自分の時間 --> ダッシュボード`\\ に移動して"
"アクセスできます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/my_time.rst:21
msgid ""
"The dashboard shows a summary of the user's time off, and the entire current "
"year, with the current day highlighted in a red circle."
msgstr ""
"ダッシュボードには、ユーザの休暇の概要と現在の年全体が表示され、現在の日が赤"
"い円形で強調表示されます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/my_time.rst:24
msgid ""
"To change the view, click on the :guilabel:`Year` button to reveal a drop-"
"down menu. Then, select either :guilabel:`Day`, :guilabel:`Week`, "
"or :guilabel:`Month` to present the calendar in that corresponding view."
msgstr ""
"表示を変更するには、\\ :guilabel:`年`\\ ボタンをクリックして"
"ドロップダウンメニューを表示します。次に、\\ :guilabel:`日`\\ 、\\ "
":guilabel:`週`\\ 、または\\ :guilabel:`月`\\ を選択して、カレンダーを対応する"
"表示で表示します。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/my_time.rst:29
msgid ""
"To change the displayed dates, click the :icon:`fa-arrow-"
"left` :guilabel:`(left arrow)` or :icon:`fa-arrow-right` :guilabel:`(right "
"arrow)` icons to the left of the :guilabel:`Year` button. The calendar view "
"adjusts in increments of the selected view."
msgstr ""
"表示する日付を変更するには、\\ :guilabel:`年`\\ ボタンの左にある\\ :icon:`fa-"
"arrow-left`\\ :guilabel:`(左矢印)`\\ または\\ :icon:`fa-arrow-right`\\ "
":guilabel:`(右矢印)`\\ アイコンをクリックします。カレンダー表示は、選択した表"
"示の単位で調整されます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/my_time.rst:33
msgid ""
"For example, if :guilabel:`Year` is selected, the arrows adjust the view by "
"one year."
msgstr ""
"たとえば、\\ :guilabel:`年`\\ が選択されている場合、矢印は表示を1年単位で調整"
"します。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/my_time.rst:35
msgid ""
"To reset the view, so it includes the current date, click "
"the :guilabel:`Today` button."
msgstr ""
"現在の日付を含むように表示をリセットするには、\\ :guilabel:`今日`\\ ボタンを"
"クリックします。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/my_time.rst:37
msgid ""
"Above the calendar view is a summary of the user's time off balances. Every "
"time off type that has been allocated appears in its own summary box. Each "
"summary lists the type of time off, the corresponding icon, the current "
"available balance (in hours or days), and an expiration date (if applicable)."
msgstr ""
"カレンダー表示の上には、ユーザの休暇残高の概要が表示されます。割り当てられた"
"すべての休暇タイプが、独自の概要ボックスに表示されます。各概要には、休暇の"
"タイプ、対応するアイコン、現在の対応可能な残高(時間または日数)、および有効期"
"限(該当する場合)がリストされます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/my_time.rst:42
msgid ""
"To view the full details of a time off balance, click the :icon:`fa-question-"
"circle-o` :guilabel:`(question mark)` icon at the end of "
"the :guilabel:`(DAYS/HOURS) AVAILABLE` on the time off summary. The complete "
"details are presented in a popover window, including "
"the :guilabel:`Allocated` time, :guilabel:`Accrual (Future)` "
"time, :guilabel:`Approved` time off scheduled, :guilabel:`Planned` time off, "
"and the currently :guilabel:`Available` time off."
msgstr ""
"休暇残高の詳細を表示するには、休暇概要の\\ :guilabel:`(日数/時間) 対応可能`\\"
" の最後にある\\ :icon:`fa-question-circle-o`\\ :guilabel:`(疑問符)`\\ "
"アイコンをクリックします。完全な詳細がポップオーバーウィンドウに表示され、\\ "
":guilabel:`割り当て`\\ 時間、\\ :guilabel:`発生(将来)`\\ 時間、スケジュール済"
"の\\ :guilabel:`承認済`\\ 休暇、\\ :guilabel:`予定済`\\ 休暇、および現在\\ "
":guilabel:`対応可能`\\ な休暇が含まれます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/my_time.rst:None
msgid "A view of the complete time off balance details in the popover window."
msgstr "ポップオーバーウィンドウでの完全な休暇残高の詳細の表示。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/my_time.rst:51
msgid ""
"A user can also select a future date to see an estimate of how much time "
"they should accrue by that point. On the right side of the time off summary "
"blocks, there is a :guilabel:`Balance at the (date)` field. Click on the "
"date, and a calendar selector popover appears."
msgstr ""
"ユーザは、将来の日付を選択して、その時点までにどれだけの時間を発生させるべき"
"かの見積もりを確認することもできます。休暇概要ブロックの右側には、\\ "
":guilabel:`(日付)時点の残高`\\ フィールドがあります。日付をクリックすると、"
"カレンダーセレクタのポップオーバーが表示されます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/my_time.rst:56
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Balance at the (date)` field **only** appears if the user is "
"accruing time off through an :doc:`accrual plan <../time_off/accrual_plans>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`(日付)時点の残高`\\ フィールドは、ユーザが\\ :doc:`休暇累積(付与"
"ルール) <../time_off/accrual_plans>`\\ を通じて休暇を累積している場合に**の"
"み**表示されます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/my_time.rst:59
msgid ""
"The current date is the default date selected. Navigate to the desired date, "
"and Odoo displays the time off balances the user should have on that date. "
"This takes into account all time off currently planned and approved. To "
"return to the current date, click the :guilabel:`Today` button to the right "
"of the date field."
msgstr ""
"現在の日付がデフォルトで選択された日付です。目的の日付に移動すると、Odoはその"
"日付にユーザが持つべき休暇残高を表示します。これには、現在予定されているすべ"
"ての休暇と承認済の休暇が考慮されます。現在の日付に戻るには、日付フィールドの"
"右側にある\\ :guilabel:`今日`\\ ボタンをクリックします。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/my_time.rst:64
msgid ""
"On the right side of the calendar, the various time off types are displayed, "
"each with their own corresponding color. The :guilabel:`Legend` explains how "
"the various statuses for time off requests are presented."
msgstr ""
"カレンダーの右側には、さまざまな休暇タイプがそれぞれ対応する色で表示されます"
"。\\ :guilabel:`凡例`\\ は、休暇申請のさまざまなステータスがどのように表示さ"
"れるかを説明しています。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/my_time.rst:68
msgid ""
"Time off that has been validated appears in a solid color. Time off requests "
"that still are still in the :guilabel:`To Approve` stage, appear with white "
"stripes in the color. :guilabel:`Refused` time off requests have a line "
"through the dates."
msgstr ""
"確認済の休暇は実線の色で表示されます。まだ\\ :guilabel:`承認待ち`\\ ステージ"
"にある休暇申請は、色に白いストライプが入って表示されます。\\ :guilabel:`却下"
"済`\\ の休暇申請は、日付に線が引かれて表示されます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/my_time.rst:72
msgid ""
"The color for each request corresponds to the specified color set with the "
"various time off types, listed in the section above the :guilabel:`Legend`."
msgstr ""
"各申請の色は、\\ :guilabel:`凡例`\\ の上のセクションにリストされているさまざ"
"まな休暇タイプで設定された指定色に対応しています。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/my_time.rst:75
msgid ""
"New time off requests can be made from the :guilabel:`Dashboard`. Click "
"the :guilabel:`New` button in the upper-left corner, and a :doc:`New Time "
"Off <request_time_off>` pop-up window appears."
msgstr ""
"新しい休暇申請は\\ :guilabel:`ダッシュボード`\\ から行うことができます。左上"
"隅の\\ :guilabel:`新規`\\ ボタンをクリックすると、\\ :doc:`新しい休暇 "
"<request_time_off>`\\ ポップアップウィンドウが表示されます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/my_time.rst:78
msgid ""
"New allocation requests can also be made from the :guilabel:`Dashboard`. "
"Click the :guilabel:`New Allocation Request` button to request more time "
"off, and a :ref:`New Allocation <time_off/request-allocation>` pop-up window "
"appears."
msgstr ""
"新しい割り当て申請も\\ :guilabel:`ダッシュボード`\\ から行うことができます"
"。\\ :guilabel:`新しい割り当て申請`\\ ボタンをクリックしてさらに休暇を申請す"
"ると、\\ :ref:`新しい割り当て <time_off/request-allocation>`\\ "
"ポップアップウィンドウが表示されます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/my_time.rst:None
msgid ""
"Time off dashboard view with the legend, time off summaries, and view "
"buttons highlighted."
msgstr ""
"休暇ダッシュボードビューで凡例、休暇サマリー、ビューボタンが強調表示されてい"
"ます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/my_time.rst:88
msgid "My time off"
msgstr "自分の休暇"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/my_time.rst:90
msgid ""
"To view a list of all the signed-in user's time off requests, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Time Off app --> My Time --> My Time Off`. Here, all time "
"off requests, both past and present, appear in a list view, grouped by month."
msgstr ""
"サインイン中のユーザのすべての休暇申請のリストを表示するには"
"、:menuselection:`休暇アプリ --> 自分の時間 --> 自分の休暇`に移動します。ここ"
"では、過去と現在のすべての休暇申請がリストビューに表示され、月ごとにグループ"
"化されます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/my_time.rst:94
msgid ""
"The list includes the following information for each request: "
"the :guilabel:`Time Off Type`, :guilabel:`Description`, :guilabel:`Start "
"Date`, :guilabel:`End Date`, :guilabel:`Duration`, and :guilabel:`Status`."
msgstr ""
"リストには、各申請について次の情報が含まれます：:guilabel:`休暇"
"タイプ`、:guilabel:`説明`、:guilabel:`開始日`、:guilabel:`終了"
"日`、:guilabel:`期間`、:guilabel:`ステータス`。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/my_time.rst:98
msgid ""
"A new time off request can be made from this view. Click the :guilabel:`New` "
"button to :doc:`request_time_off`."
msgstr ""
"このビューから新しい休暇申請を行うことができます。:guilabel:`新規`ボタンを"
"クリックして:doc:`request_time_off`。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/my_time.rst:None
msgid "My Time list view with all requests."
msgstr "すべての申請を含む自分の時間リストビュー。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/my_time.rst:107
msgid "My allocations"
msgstr "自分の付与"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/my_time.rst:109
msgid ""
"To view a list of all allocations, navigate to :menuselection:`Time Off app "
"--> My Time --> My Allocations`. All allocations and requested allocations "
"appear in a list view."
msgstr ""
"すべての付与のリストを表示するには、:menuselection:`休暇アプリ --> 自分の時"
"間 --> 自分の付与`に移動します。すべての付与と申請された付与がリストビューに"
"表示されます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/my_time.rst:112
msgid ""
"The information presented on the :guilabel:`My Allocations` page "
"includes: :guilabel:`Time Off "
"Type`, :guilabel:`Amount`, :guilabel:`Allocation Type`, :guilabel:`Accrual "
"Plan`, and :guilabel:`Status`. If the signed-in user has the appropriate "
"access rights, they may also see an option to :guilabel:`Approve` requests, "
"if applicable."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`自分の付与`ページに表示される情報には、:guilabel:`休暇"
"タイプ`、:guilabel:`付与数`、:guilabel:`付与タイプ`、:guilabel:`累積"
"プラン`、:guilabel:`ステータス`が含まれます。サインイン中のユーザが適切な"
"アクセス権を持っている場合、該当する場合は申請を:guilabel:`承認`する"
"オプションも表示されることがあります。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/my_time.rst:117
msgid ""
"A new allocation request can be made from this view, as well. Click "
"the :guilabel:`New` button to :ref:`request an allocation <time_off/request-"
"allocation>`."
msgstr ""
"このビューから新しい付与申請を行うこともできます。:guilabel:`新規`ボタンを"
"クリックして:ref:`付与を申請 <time_off/request-allocation>`します。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/my_time.rst:None
msgid "My Allocations list view with all requests."
msgstr "すべての申請を含む自分の付与リストビュー。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/public_holidays.rst:3
msgid "Public holidays"
msgstr "祭日"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/public_holidays.rst:5
msgid ""
"Since holidays vary by country, region, and even city, Odoo's **Time Off** "
"app does *not* include any public holidays by default. To account for public "
"or national holidays, configure the observed holidays in Odoo so employees "
"can receive the appropriate days off."
msgstr ""
"休日は国、地域、さらには都市によって異なるため、Odoōの**休暇**アプリには"
"デフォルトで祝日が含まれて*いません*。公休日や祝日を考慮するには、Odooで観察"
"される休日を設定し、従業員が適切な休日を受け取れるようにします。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/public_holidays.rst:9
msgid ""
"Configuring public holidays helps employees clearly see their non-working "
"days and prevents unnecessary time off requests for dates already designated "
"as holidays."
msgstr ""
"祝日を設定することで、従業員は非勤務日を明確に確認でき、すでに休日として指定"
"されている日付に対して不要な休暇申請を防ぐことができます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/public_holidays.rst:12
msgid ""
"Public holidays configured in the **Time Off** app are also reflected across "
"other Odoo apps that use :doc:`working schedules <../payroll/"
"working_schedules>`, including **Calendar**, **Planning**, "
"**Manufacturing**, and more."
msgstr ""
"**休暇**アプリで設定された祝日は、**カレンダー**、**計画**、**製造**など、\\ "
":doc:`勤務時間 <../payroll/working_schedules>`\\ を使用する他のOdooアプリ全体"
"にも反映されます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/public_holidays.rst:16
msgid ""
"Because of Odoo's integration across these apps, configuring all public "
"holidays is considered best practice."
msgstr ""
"これらのアプリ間のOdooの統合により、すべての祝日を設定することが"
"ベストプラクティスと見なされます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/public_holidays.rst:20
msgid "Create public holidays"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/public_holidays.rst:22
msgid ""
"To create a public holiday, navigate to :menuselection:`Time Off app --> "
"Configuration --> Public Holidays`. All currently configured public holidays "
"appear in a default list view."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/public_holidays.rst:25
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`New` button and a new line appears at the bottom of the "
"list."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`新規`\\ ボタンをクリックすると、リストの下部に新しい行が表示されま"
"す。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/public_holidays.rst:29
msgid ":guilabel:`Name`: Enter the name of the holiday."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/public_holidays.rst:30
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Company`: If in a multi-company database, the current company "
"populates this field by default. It is **not** possible to edit this field."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/public_holidays.rst:34
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Company` field is hidden, by default. To view this field, "
"click the :icon:`oi-settings-adjust` :guilabel:`(settings adjusts)` icon in "
"the top-right corner of the list, to the far-right of the column titles, and "
"activate the :guilabel:`Company` selection from the drop-down menu that "
"appears."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/public_holidays.rst:39
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Start Date`: Using the date and time picker, select the date and "
"time the holiday starts, then click :guilabel:`Apply`. By default, this "
"field is configured for the current date, with a start time of `12:00 AM`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`開始日`\\ :日付と時刻ピッカーを使用して、休日が始まる日付と時刻を"
"選択し、\\ :guilabel:`適用`\\ をクリックします。デフォルトでは、この"
"フィールドは現在の日付で、開始時刻は`12:00 AM`に設定されています。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/public_holidays.rst:42
msgid ""
":guilabel:`End Date`: Using the date and time picker, select the date and "
"time the holiday ends, then click :guilabel:`Apply`. By default, this field "
"is configured for the current date, with an end time of `11:59 PM`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`終了日`\\ :日付と時刻ピッカーを使用して、休日が終了する日付と時刻"
"を選択し、\\ :guilabel:`適用`\\ をクリックします。デフォルトでは、この"
"フィールドは現在の日付で、終了時刻は`11:59 PM`に設定されています。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/public_holidays.rst:47
msgid ""
"It is **not** recommended to change the public holiday hours of `12:00 AM` "
"to `11:59 PM`. This ensures all employees working all shifts receive the "
"public holiday."
msgstr ""
"祝日の時間を`12:00 AM`から`11:59 PM`に変更することは**推奨されません**。これ"
"により、すべてのシフトで勤務するすべての従業員が祝日を受け取ることが保証され"
"ます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/public_holidays.rst:50
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Working Hours`: If the holiday should only apply to employees who "
"have a specific set of working hours, select the working hours using the "
"drop-down menu. If left blank, the holiday applies to all employees."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`勤務時間`\\ :休日が特定の勤務時間を持つ従業員にのみ適用される場合"
"は、ドロップダウンメニューを使用して勤務時間を選択します。空白のままにすると"
"、休日はすべての従業員に適用されます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/public_holidays.rst:53
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Work Entry Type`: If using the **Payroll** app, this field "
"defines how the :doc:`work entries <../payroll/work_entries>` for the "
"holiday appear. Select the work entry type using the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`勤務記録タイプ`\\ :**給与**アプリを使用している場合、この"
"フィールドは休日の\\ :doc:`勤務記録 <../payroll/work_entries>`\\ がどのように"
"表示されるかを定義します。ドロップダウンメニューを使用して勤務記録タイプを選"
"択します。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/public_holidays.rst:None
msgid "The list of public holidays in the configuration menu."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/reporting.rst:5
msgid ""
"The **Time Off** app's reporting feature lets managers view team time off by "
"employee, type, or remaining balances. This allows managers to see :ref:`who "
"is taking time off, how much they have used <time_off/by-"
"employee>`, :ref:`which types are more commonly used <time_off/by_type>`, "
"and :ref:`how much each employee still has available <time_off/balance>`."
msgstr ""
"**休暇**アプリのレポーティング機能により、マネージャーは従業員、タイプ、また"
"は残高別にチームの休暇を表示できます。これにより、マネージャーは:ref:`誰が休"
"暇を取得しているか、どれだけ使用したか <time_off/by-employee>`、:ref:`どの"
"タイプがより一般的に使用されているか <time_off/by_type>`、および:ref:`各従業"
"員がまだどれだけ対応可能か <time_off/balance>`を確認できます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/reporting.rst:10
msgid ""
"Any report can be added to a spreadsheet, when in either the :icon:`fa-area-"
"chart` :guilabel:`(Graph)` or :icon:`oi-view-pivot` :guilabel:`(Pivot)` "
"view, through the *Insert in Spreadsheet* button that appears in the top-"
"left of a report."
msgstr ""
":icon:`fa-area-chart` :guilabel:`(グラフ)`または:icon:`oi-view-pivot` "
":guilabel:`(ピボット)`ビューのいずれかで、レポートの左上に表示され"
"る*スプレッドシートに挿入*ボタンを使用して、任意のレポートをスプレッドシート"
"に追加できます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/reporting.rst:15
msgid ""
"If the **Documents** app is installed, an option to add the report to a "
"spreadsheet appears. If not, the report can be added to a *Dashboard*."
msgstr ""
"**ドキュメント**アプリがインストールされている場合、レポートを"
"スプレッドシートに追加するオプションが表示されます。インストールされていない"
"場合は、レポートを*ダッシュボード*に追加できます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/reporting.rst:21
msgid "By employee"
msgstr "従業員別"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/reporting.rst:23
msgid ""
"Viewing time off by employee helps managers track usage patterns, monitor "
"remaining balances, ensure policy compliance, and plan coverage for upcoming "
"absences. To view a list of employee time off requests, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Time Off app --> Reporting --> by Employee`."
msgstr ""
"従業員別に休暇を表示することで、マネージャーは使用パターンの追跡、残高の監視"
"、ポリシーコンプライアンスの確保、および今後の欠勤に対するカバレッジの計画を"
"行うことができます。従業員の休暇申請のリストを表示するには"
"、:menuselection:`休暇アプリ --> レポーティング --> 従業員別`に移動します。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/reporting.rst:27
msgid ""
"The default report presents the current year's data in a list view, "
"displaying all the employees in alphabetical order. Each employee's line is "
"collapsed by default. To expand a line, click anywhere on the line."
msgstr ""
"デフォルトのレポートは、現在の年のデータをリストビューで表示し、すべての従業"
"員をアルファベット順に表示します。各従業員の行はデフォルトで折りたたまれてい"
"ます。行を展開するには、行の任意の場所をクリックします。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/reporting.rst:31
msgid ""
"The view expands, and has the time off requests organized by time off type. "
"Click anywhere on a time off type line to expand it, and view all the "
"individual time off requests that fall under that type."
msgstr ""
"ビューが展開され、休暇申請が休暇タイプ別に整理されます。休暇タイプの行の任意"
"の場所をクリックして展開し、そのタイプに該当するすべての個別の休暇申請を表示"
"します。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/reporting.rst:34
msgid ""
"The information shown in the list includes: the :guilabel:`Employee` "
"name, :guilabel:`Number of Days` off requested, the :guilabel:`Start "
"Date`, :guilabel:`End Date`, :guilabel:`Status`, and :guilabel:`Description`."
msgstr ""
"リストに表示される情報には、:guilabel:`従業員`名、申請された:guilabel:`日"
"数`、:guilabel:`開始日`、:guilabel:`終了"
"日`、:guilabel:`ステータス`、:guilabel:`説明`が含まれます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/reporting.rst:None
msgid "Report of time off, shown by each employee in a list view."
msgstr "リストビューで各従業員別に表示された休暇のレポート。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/reporting.rst:41
msgid ""
"The report can be displayed in other ways, as well. Click the corresponding "
"button option in the top-right corner of the page to view the data in that "
"specific way. The various options are a :icon:`oi-view-"
"list` :guilabel:`(List)`, or default view, :icon:`fa-area-"
"chart` :guilabel:`(Graph)`, :icon:`oi-view-pivot` :guilabel:`(Pivot)` table, "
"or :icon:`fa-calendar` :guilabel:`(Calendar)` view."
msgstr ""
"レポートは他の方法でも表示できます。ページの右上隅にある対応する"
"ボタンオプションをクリックすると、その特定の方法でデータを表示できます。さま"
"ざまなオプションは、:icon:`oi-view-list`\\ :guilabel:`リスト`（または"
"デフォルトビュー）、:icon:`fa-area-chart`\\ :guilabel:`グラフ`、:icon:`oi-"
"view-pivot`\\ :guilabel:`ピボット`\\ テーブル、または:icon:`fa-calendar`\\ "
":guilabel:`カレンダー`\\ ビューです。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/reporting.rst:46
msgid ""
"When a selection has been made, additional options appear for that "
"particular selection. For more detailed information on the reports and their "
"various options, refer to the :doc:`reporting <../../essentials/reporting>` "
"documentation."
msgstr ""
"選択が行われると、その特定の選択に対する追加オプションが表示されます。"
"レポートとそのさまざまなオプションに関する詳細情報については"
"、:doc:`レポーティング <../../essentials/reporting>`\\ のドキュメントを参照し"
"てください。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/reporting.rst:53
msgid "By type"
msgstr "タイプごと"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/reporting.rst:55
msgid ""
"Viewing company-wide time off by type can help managers determine if "
"employees are using their time off, which types are used more than others, "
"and can spot any trends. High totals in certain time off types, like sick "
"time off, can indicate health or morale concerns."
msgstr ""
"タイプ別に会社全体の休暇を表示することで、マネジャーは従業員が休暇を使用して"
"いるかどうか、どのタイプが他のタイプよりも多く使用されているか、および傾向を"
"発見することができます。病気休暇などの特定の休暇タイプで合計が高い場合、健康"
"や士気の問題を示している可能性があります。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/reporting.rst:59
msgid ""
"To view a graph of all time off, organized by time off type, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Time Off app --> Reporting --> by Type`. This shows all "
"time off requests in a default bar chart."
msgstr ""
"休暇タイプ別に整理されたすべての休暇のグラフを表示するには"
"、:menuselection:`休暇アプリ --> レポーティング --> タイプ別`\\ に移動します"
"。これにより、すべての休暇申請がデフォルトの棒グラフで表示されます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/reporting.rst:62
msgid ""
"Hover over a bar to view the :guilabel:`Duration (Days)` of that specific "
"time off type."
msgstr ""
"バーにカーソルを合わせると、その特定の休暇タイプの:guilabel:`期間（日数）`\\ "
"が表示されます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/reporting.rst:None
msgid ""
"The various time off types, and how many days requested, in a bar chart. "
"Details are\n"
"highlighted in a red box."
msgstr ""
"さまざまな休暇タイプと申請された日数が棒グラフで表示されます。詳細は赤い"
"ボックスで強調表示されています。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/reporting.rst:68
msgid ""
"Click on a bar to go to a detailed list view of all the time off requests "
"for that time off type."
msgstr ""
"バーをクリックすると、その休暇タイプのすべての休暇申請の詳細なリストビューに"
"移動します。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/reporting.rst:70
msgid ""
"Each request is listed, with the following information displayed: "
"the :guilabel:`Employee`, :guilabel:`Number of Days`, :guilabel:`Request "
"Type`, :guilabel:`Start Date`, :guilabel:`End Date`, :guilabel:`Status`, and "
"the :guilabel:`Description`."
msgstr ""
"各申請がリストされ、次の情報が表示されます：:guilabel:`従業員`、:guilabel:`日"
"数`、:guilabel:`申請タイプ`、:guilabel:`開始日`、:guilabel:`終了"
"日`、:guilabel:`ステータス`、および:guilabel:`説明`。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/reporting.rst:74
msgid ""
"The report can be displayed in other ways, as well. Click the corresponding "
"button option in the top-right corner of the page to view the data in that "
"way. The various options are a :icon:`fa-area-chart` :guilabel:`(Graph)` "
"(the default view), :icon:`oi-view-list` :guilabel:`(List)`, or :icon:`oi-"
"view-pivot` :guilabel:`(Pivot)` table."
msgstr ""
"レポートは他の方法でも表示できます。ページの右上隅にある対応する"
"ボタンオプションをクリックすると、その方法でデータを表示できます。さまざまな"
"オプションは、:icon:`fa-area-chart`\\ :guilabel:`グラフ`（デフォルトビュー）"
"、:icon:`oi-view-list`\\ :guilabel:`リスト`、または:icon:`oi-view-pivot`\\ "
":guilabel:`ピボット`\\ テーブルです。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/reporting.rst:79
msgid ""
"When a selection has been made, additional options appear for that "
"particular selection. For more detailed information on the reports, and "
"their various options, refer to the :doc:`reporting <../../essentials/"
"reporting>` documentation."
msgstr ""
"選択が行われると、その特定の選択に対する追加オプションが表示されます。"
"レポートとそのさまざまなオプションに関する詳細情報については"
"、:doc:`レポーティング <../../essentials/reporting>`\\ のドキュメントを参照し"
"てください。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/reporting.rst:86
msgid "Balance"
msgstr "残高"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/reporting.rst:88
msgid ""
"When some time off types have restrictions, such as rollover rules and "
"balance limits, viewing time off balances can help managers see a high-level "
"overview of time off. If certain employees have a lot of time that will "
"expire soon, they can inform their employees and adjust scheduled "
"accordingly to be prepared for their absences."
msgstr ""
"一部の休暇タイプには、繰越ルールや残高制限などの制限がある場合、休暇残高を表"
"示することで、マネジャーは休暇の高レベルな概要を確認できます。特定の従業員が"
"間もなく失効する多くの時間を持っている場合、マネジャーは従業員に通知し、不在"
"に備えてスケジュールを調整できます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/reporting.rst:93
msgid ""
"To view a pivot table of all time off balances, organized by time off type, "
"then further organized by how many days and hours are :guilabel:`Left` "
"and :guilabel:`Planned`, navigate to :menuselection:`Time Off app --> "
"Reporting --> Balance`."
msgstr ""
"休暇タイプ別に整理され、さらに:guilabel:`残`\\ と:guilabel:`スケジュール済`\\"
" の日数と時間数別に整理されたすべての休暇残高のピボットテーブルを表示するには"
"、:menuselection:`休暇アプリ --> レポーティング --> 残高`\\ に移動します。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/reporting.rst:97
msgid ""
"This shows all time off balances in a default pivot table. The employees "
"populate the rows, while the various time off types and balances populate "
"the columns."
msgstr ""
"これにより、すべての休暇残高がデフォルトのピボットテーブルで表示されます。従"
"業員が行に入力され、さまざまな休暇タイプと残高が列に入力されます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/reporting.rst:None
msgid "The various time off balances, in a pivot table."
msgstr "さまざまな休暇残高がピボットテーブルで表示されます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/request_time_off.rst:3
msgid "Request time off"
msgstr "休暇を申請する"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/request_time_off.rst:5
msgid ""
"When employees wish to take time off, they first submit a time off request "
"through the **Time Off** application. Once their request has been submitted, "
"it is then reviewed by either the employee's manager or their time off "
"officer (depending on who the employee's :ref:`time off approver is "
"<employees/approvers>`)."
msgstr ""
"従業員が休暇を取得したい場合、まず**休暇**アプリケーションを通じて休暇申請を"
"提出します。申請が提出されると、従業員のマネジャーまたは休暇担当者（従業員"
"の:ref:`休暇承認者 <employees/approvers>`\\ が誰であるかによって異なります）"
"によって確認されます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/request_time_off.rst:11
msgid ""
"If the time off type the employee is requesting :ref:`does not require "
"approval <time_off/time-off-requests>`, the time off is automatically "
"approved, and does not need to be reviewed."
msgstr ""
"従業員が申請している休暇タイプが:ref:`承認を必要としない <time_off/time-off-"
"requests>`\\ 場合、休暇は自動的に承認され、確認する必要はありません。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/request_time_off.rst:16
msgid "Submit time off request"
msgstr "休暇申請を提出する"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/request_time_off.rst:18
msgid ""
"To request time off, click the :guilabel:`New` button in the top-left corner "
"of the **Time Off** app dashboard, and a :guilabel:`New Time Off` pop-up "
"form loads."
msgstr ""
"休暇を申請するには、**休暇**アプリダッシュボードの左上隅にある:guilabel:`新"
"規`\\ ボタンをクリックすると、:guilabel:`新規休暇`\\ ポップアップフォームが読"
"み込まれます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/request_time_off.rst:21
msgid ""
"Fill out the :ref:`fields on the form <time_off/fields>`, and then "
"click :guilabel:`Save & Close` to submit the request."
msgstr ""
"フォームの:ref:`フィールドに記入 <time_off/fields>`\\ し、:guilabel:`保存して"
"閉じる`\\ をクリックして申請を提出します。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/request_time_off.rst:25
msgid ""
"Requesting time off can be done either form the main **Time Off** app "
"dashboard, or by navigating to :menuselection:`Time Off --> My Time --> My "
"Time Off`, and clicking :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"休暇の申請は、メインの\\ **休暇**\\ アプリのダッシュボードから行うか"
"、:menuselection:`休暇 --> マイ休暇 --> マイ休暇`に移動して:guilabel:`新規`を"
"クリックして行います。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/request_time_off.rst:None
msgid "A time off request for three hours of vacation time off."
msgstr "3時間の有給休暇の休暇申請。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/request_time_off.rst:34
msgid "Time off fields"
msgstr "休暇フィールド"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/request_time_off.rst:36
msgid ""
"Enter the following information on the :guilabel:`New Time Off` request form:"
msgstr ":guilabel:`新規休暇`申請フォームに次の情報を入力します："

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/request_time_off.rst:38
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Time Off Type`: Using the drop-down menu, select the type of time "
"off being requested."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`休暇タイプ`：ドロップダウンメニューから、申請する休暇のタイプを選"
"択します。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/request_time_off.rst:39
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Dates`: Enter the dates that the time off falls under. There are "
"two fields to populate: the start and end dates. Click on either date field "
"and a popover calendar appears."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`日付`：休暇が該当する日付を入力します。入力するフィールドは2つあり"
"ます：開始日と終了日です。いずれかの日付フィールドをクリックすると、"
"ポップオーバーカレンダーが表示されます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/request_time_off.rst:42
msgid ""
"Click on the start date, then click on the end date. The selected start and "
"end dates are circled, and the dates between them are highlighted (if "
"applicable)."
msgstr ""
"開始日をクリックしてから、終了日をクリックします。選択した開始日と終了日は丸"
"で囲まれ、その間の日付が強調表示されます（該当する場合）。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/request_time_off.rst:45
msgid ""
"If only requesting time off for a single day, click on the start date, then "
"click the same date again for the end date."
msgstr ""
"1日のみの休暇を申請する場合は、開始日をクリックしてから、終了日として同じ日付"
"を再度クリックします。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/request_time_off.rst:48
msgid ""
"When the correct dates are selected, click the :guilabel:`Apply` button."
msgstr "正しい日付が選択されたら、:guilabel:`適用`ボタンをクリックします。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/request_time_off.rst:50
msgid ""
"The selected dates now populate the two portions of the :guilabel:`Dates` "
"field."
msgstr "選択した日付が:guilabel:`日付`フィールドの2つの部分に入力されます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/request_time_off.rst:52
msgid ""
"If the selected :guilabel:`Time Off Type` is configured to have the time off "
"taken in hours, the following two fields also appear:"
msgstr ""
"選択した:guilabel:`休暇タイプ`が時間単位で休暇を取得するように設定されている"
"場合、次の2つのフィールドも表示されます："

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/request_time_off.rst:55
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Half Day`: If the time off request is for a half day, tick this "
"checkbox. When this is selected, the second date field disappears, and is "
"replaced with a drop-down menu. From that drop-down menu, select "
"either :guilabel:`Morning` or :guilabel:`Afternoon` to indicate which half "
"of the day is being requested off."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`半日`：休暇申請が半日の場合は、このチェックボックスをオンにします"
"。これを選択すると、2番目の日付フィールドが消え、ドロップダウンメニューに置き"
"換えられます。そのドロップダウンメニューから:guilabel:`午前`また"
"は:guilabel:`午後`を選択して、1日のどちらの半分を休暇申請するかを示します。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/request_time_off.rst:59
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Custom Hours`: If the time off requested is not a whole or half "
"day, tick this checkbox. If selected, a :guilabel:`From` and :guilabel:`To` "
"field appears beneath this option. Using the drop-down menu, select the "
"start and end time for the time off request."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`カスタム時間`：申請する休暇が丸一日または半日でない場合は、この"
"チェックボックスをオンにします。選択すると、このオプションの下に:guilabel:`移"
"動元`と:guilabel:`移動先`フィールドが表示されます。ドロップダウンメニューを使"
"用して、休暇申請の開始時刻と終了時刻を選択します。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/request_time_off.rst:63
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Requested (Days/Hours)`: This field updates automatically once "
"the :guilabel:`Date` section is completed. If the :guilabel:`Date` section "
"is modified, this section automatically updates to reflect the total time "
"off requested. This field is in either hours or days, depending on how the "
"selected :doc:`Time Off Type <../time_off/time_off_types>` is configured."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`申請済み（日数/時間）`：このフィールドは、:guilabel:`日"
"付`セクションが完了すると自動的に更新されます。:guilabel:`日付`セクションが変"
"更されると、このセクションは申請された休暇の合計を反映するように自動的に更新"
"されます。このフィールドは、選択された:doc:`休暇タイプ <../time_off/"
"time_off_types>`の設定方法に応じて、時間または日数で表示されます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/request_time_off.rst:67
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Description`: Enter a description for the time off request. This "
"should include any details that managers and approvers may need to approve "
"the request."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`説明`：休暇申請の説明を入力します。これには、管理者や承認者が申請"
"を承認するために必要な詳細を含める必要があります。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/request_time_off.rst:69
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Supporting Document`: This field **only** appears if "
"the :doc:`Time Off Type <../time_off/time_off_types>` selected allows for "
"the attachment of documents. Click the :icon:`fa-"
"paperclip` :guilabel:`Attach File` button, and a file explorer window "
"appears."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`補足ドキュメント`：このフィールドは、選択された:doc:`休暇タイプ "
"<../time_off/time_off_types>`がドキュメントの添付を許可している場合**のみ**表"
"示されます。:icon:`fa-paperclip` :guilabel:`ファイルを添付`ボタンをクリックす"
"ると、ファイルエクスプローラーウィンドウが表示されます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/request_time_off.rst:73
msgid ""
"Navigate to the desired files that should be attached, select them, then "
"click The :guilabel:`Open` button. The files then appear on the time off "
"request form. Multiple documents can be attached, if necessary."
msgstr ""
"添付するファイルに移動して選択し、:guilabel:`開く`ボタンをクリックします。"
"ファイルが休暇申請フォームに表示されます。必要に応じて、複数のドキュメントを"
"添付できます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/request_time_off.rst:None
msgid ""
"A time off request form filled out for an employee home sick with the flu."
msgstr "インフルエンザで病欠した従業員のために記入された休暇申請フォーム。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:5
msgid ""
"One of the first things that requires configuration in the **Time Off** app "
"are the time off types."
msgstr "**休暇**アプリで最初に設定が必要なものの1つは、休暇タイプです。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:7
msgid ""
"When employees request time off, they must specify the *type* of time off "
"they are requesting, such as sick time, vacation time, etc. The time off "
"type determines several things, including *how* the request is made (hours, "
"half days, or days), and how it is :ref:`approved <time_off/time-off-"
"requests>`."
msgstr ""
"従業員が休暇を申請する際には、病欠や休暇など、申請する休暇の\\ *種類*\\ を指"
"定する必要があります。休暇の種類により、申請方法（時間、半日、または日数）"
"や\\ :ref:`承認 <time_off/time-off-requests>`\\ 方法などが決まります。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:12
msgid ""
"To view the currently configured time off types, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Time Off app --> Configuration --> Time Off Types`. The "
"time off types are presented in a list view."
msgstr ""
"現在設定されている休暇タイプを表示するには、:menuselection:`休暇アプリ --> 設"
"定 --> 休暇タイプ`\\ に移動します。休暇タイプはリストビューで表示されます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:15
msgid ""
"The **Time Off** app comes with six preconfigured time off "
"types: :guilabel:`Paid Time Off`, :guilabel:`Sick Time "
"Off`, :guilabel:`Unpaid`, :guilabel:`Compensatory Days`, :guilabel:`Extra "
"Time Off`, and :guilabel:`Extra Hours`. These can be modified to suit "
"business needs, or used as-is."
msgstr ""
"**休暇**\\ アプリには、6つの事前設定された休暇タイプが用意されています"
"：:guilabel:`有給休暇`、:guilabel:`病気休暇`、:guilabel:`未払`、:guilabel:`代"
"休`、:guilabel:`特別休暇`、:guilabel:`追加勤務時間`。これらはビジネスニーズに"
"合わせて変更することも、そのまま使用することもできます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:20
msgid "Create time off type"
msgstr "休暇タイプの作成"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:22
msgid ""
"To create a new time off type, navigate to :menuselection:`Time Off app --> "
"Configuration --> Time Off Types`. From here, click the :guilabel:`New` "
"button to reveal a blank *Time Off Type* form. Then, enter the following "
"information on the form."
msgstr ""
"新しい休暇タイプを作成するには、:menuselection:`休暇アプリ --> 設定 --> 休暇"
"タイプ`\\ に移動します。ここから、:guilabel:`新規`\\ ボタンをクリックして、空"
"白の\\ *休暇タイプ*\\ フォームを表示します。次に、フォームに以下の情報を入力"
"します。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:27
msgid ""
"The only **required** configurations on the time off type form are the "
"following fields:"
msgstr "休暇タイプフォームで\\ **必須**\\ の設定は、以下のフィールドのみです："

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:29
msgid ":guilabel:`Time Off Type`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`休暇タイプ`"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:30
msgid ":guilabel:`Duration Type`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`期間タイプ`"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:31
msgid ":guilabel:`Count as`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`カウント基準`"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:32
msgid ":guilabel:`Approval`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`承認`"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:37
msgid ""
"This section outlines the high-level information for the time off type. "
"Enter the following information at the top of the form:"
msgstr ""
"このセクションでは、休暇タイプの高レベル情報の概要を説明します。フォームの上"
"部に以下の情報を入力します："

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:40
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Time Off Type`: Enter the name for the particular type of time "
"off, such as `Vacation` or `Bereavement`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`休暇タイプ`：特定の休暇タイプの名前を入力します。例：`休暇`また"
"は`忌引`。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:42
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Duration Type`: Select the format the time off is requested in by "
"clicking the corresponding radio button. The options are:"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`期間タイプ`：対応するラジオボタンをクリックして、休暇を申請する形"
"式を選択します。オプションは次のとおりです："

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:45
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Day`: Time off can only be requested in full-day increments (8 "
"hours)."
msgstr ":guilabel:`日`：休暇は全日単位（8時間）でのみ申請できます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:46
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Half Day`: Time off can only be requested in half-day increments "
"(4 hours)."
msgstr ":guilabel:`半日`：休暇は半日単位（4時間）でのみ申請できます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:47
msgid ":guilabel:`Hours`: Time off can be taken in hourly increments."
msgstr ":guilabel:`時間`：休暇は時間単位で取得できます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:49
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Count as`: Using the drop-down menu, select whether the time off "
"type is counted toward accrual plans. Select :guilabel:`Worked Time` if the "
"time off *does* count, select :guilabel:`Absence` if it does *not* count "
"toward any type of accrual."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`カウント基準`：ドロップダウンメニューを使用して、休暇タイプが休暇"
"累積（付与ルール）にカウントされるかどうかを選択します。時間が\\ *カウントさ"
"れる*\\ 場合は:guilabel:`勤務時間`\\ を選択し、あらゆる種類の累積に\\ "
"*カウントされない*\\ 場合は:guilabel:`休暇`\\ を選択します。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:52
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Notify HR`: Select the user who is notified and responsible for "
"approving requests and allocations for this specific type of time off. If "
"this field is left blank, no one is notified."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`HR通知`：この特定の休暇タイプのリクエストと割り当ての承認を担当し"
"、通知されるユーザを選択します。このフィールドが空白の場合、誰にも通知されま"
"せん。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:54
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Company`: If :doc:`multiple companies are created in the database "
"<../../general/companies/multi_company>`, and this time off type only "
"applies to one company, select the company from the drop-down menu. If this "
"field is left blank, the time off type applies to all companies in the "
"database. This field **only** appears in a multi-company database."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`会社`：:doc:`データベースに複数の会社が作成されている <../../"
"general/companies/multi_company>`\\ 場合で、この休暇タイプが1つの会社にのみ適"
"用される場合は、ドロップダウンメニューから会社を選択します。このフィールドを"
"空白のままにすると、休暇タイプはデータベース内のすべての会社に適用されます。"
"このフィールドは、マルチカンパニー\\ データベースでのみ表示されます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:58
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Country`: If multiple countries are associated with the database, "
"and this time off type is restricted to one country, select the country from "
"the drop-down menu. If this field is left blank, the time off type applies "
"to all countries. This field **only** appears in a multi-country database."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`国`：データベースに複数の国が関連付けられており、この休暇タイプが1"
"つの国に制限されている場合は、ドロップダウンメニューから国を選択します。この"
"フィールドを空白のままにすると、休暇タイプはすべての国に適用されます。この"
"フィールドは、複数の国のデータベースでのみ表示されます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:None
msgid ""
"The top half of the time off type form, with all the generic information "
"populated."
msgstr "休暇タイプフォームの上半分で、すべての一般情報が入力されています。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:69
msgid "Time off requests section"
msgstr "休暇申請セクション"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:71
msgid ""
"This section determines how approvals are handled for time off requests for "
"this time off type."
msgstr ""
"このセクションでは、この休暇タイプの休暇申請に対する承認の処理方法を決定しま"
"す。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:73
msgid ""
"Select what specific kind of :guilabel:`Approval` is required for the time "
"off type. The options are:"
msgstr ""
"休暇タイプに必要な特定の種類の:guilabel:`承認`\\ を選択します。オプションは次"
"のとおりです："

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:76
msgid ""
":guilabel:`None Needed`: No approvals are required when requesting this type "
"of time off. The time off request is automatically approved."
msgstr ""
"\\ :guilabel:`承認なし`\\ ：この種類の休暇を申請する際、承認は不要です。休暇"
"申請は自動的に承認されます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:78
msgid ""
":guilabel:`By Time Off Officer`: Only the specified time off officer, set on "
"this form in the :guilabel:`Notify HR` field, is required to approve the "
"time off request. This option is selected by default."
msgstr ""
"\\ :guilabel:`休暇管理者による承認`\\ ：このフォームの\\ :guilabel:`人事部に"
"通知`\\ フィールドで設定された、指定された休暇管理者のみが休暇申請を承認する"
"必要があります。このオプションはデフォルトで選択されています。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:81
msgid ""
":guilabel:`By Employee's Approver`: Only the employee's specified approver "
"for time off, which is configured in the *Settings* tab of "
"the :ref:`employee's form <employees/approvers>`, is required to approve the "
"time off request."
msgstr ""
"\\ :guilabel:`従業員の承認者による承認`\\ ：\\ :ref:`従業員フォーム "
"<employees/approvers>`\\ の*設定*タブで設定された、従業員の指定された休暇承認"
"者のみが休暇申請を承認する必要があります。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:84
msgid ""
":guilabel:`By Employee's Approver and Time Off Officer`: Both the "
"employee's :ref:`specified time off approver <employees/approvers>` and the "
"time off officer are required to approve the time off request."
msgstr ""
"\\ :guilabel:`従業員の承認者と休暇管理者による承認`\\ ：従業員の\\ :ref:`指定"
"された休暇承認者 <employees/approvers>`\\ と休暇管理者の両方が休暇申請を承認"
"する必要があります。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:89
msgid "Allocation requests section"
msgstr "割り当て申請セクション"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:91
msgid ""
"This section determines how allocation requests are handled for this time "
"off type."
msgstr "このセクションでは、この休暇タイプの割り当て申請の処理方法を決定します。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:93
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Requires allocation`: If the time off must be allocated to "
"employees, enable the checkbox. If the time off can be requested without "
"time off being previously allocated, uncheck the box. If unchecked, no other "
"options appear in the *Allocation Requests* section."
msgstr ""
"\\ :guilabel:`割当が必要`\\ ：休暇を従業員に割り当てる必要がある場合は、"
"チェックボックスを有効にします。休暇が事前に割り当てられていなくても申請でき"
"る場合は、チェックを外します。チェックを外すと、*割当申請*セクションに他の"
"オプションは表示されません。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:96
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Allow Employee Requests`: Check the checkbox if the employee "
"should be able to request more time off than was allocated."
msgstr ""
"\\ :guilabel:`従業員による申請を許可`\\ ：従業員が割り当てられた休暇よりも多"
"くの休暇を申請できるようにする場合は、チェックボックスをオンにします。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:99
msgid ""
"If employees should **not** be able to make requests for more time off than "
"what was allocated, leave the box unchecked."
msgstr ""
"従業員が割り当てられた休暇よりも多くの休暇を申請できないようにする場合は、"
"チェックを外したままにします。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:103
msgid ""
"Ten days are allocated to the employee for this particular type of time off, "
"and the :guilabel:`Allow Employee Requests` option is enabled. The employee "
"wants to take a vacation for twelve days. They may submit a request for two "
"additional days, since the :guilabel:`Allow Employee Requests` option is "
"enabled."
msgstr ""
"この特定の種類の休暇について、従業員に10日が割り当てられており、\\ "
":guilabel:`従業員による申請を許可`\\ オプションが有効になっています。従業員は"
"12日間の休暇を取得したいと考えています。\\ :guilabel:`従業員による申請を許"
"可`\\ オプションが有効になっているため、追加の2日間を申請できます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:109
msgid ""
"It is important to note that requesting additional time off does **not** "
"guarantee that time off is granted."
msgstr ""
"追加の休暇を申請しても、休暇が付与されることが保証されるわけでは\\ **ない**\\"
" ことに注意してください。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:112
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Approval`: Select the type of approvals required for the "
"allocation of this particular time off type."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`承認`: この特定の休暇タイプの割り当てに必要な承認のタイプを選択し"
"ます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:115
msgid ""
":guilabel:`None Needed`: No approvals are required when requesting "
"additional allocations for the time off type. The allocation request is "
"automatically approved."
msgstr ""
"\\ :guilabel:`承認なし`\\ ：休暇タイプの追加割当を申請する際、承認は不要です"
"。割当申請は自動的に承認されます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:117
msgid ""
":guilabel:`By Time Off Officer`: Only the specified time off officer, set on "
"this form in the :guilabel:`Notify HR` field, is required to approve the "
"allocation request. This option is selected, by default."
msgstr ""
"\\ :guilabel:`休暇管理者による承認`\\ ：このフォームの\\ :guilabel:`人事部に"
"通知`\\ フィールドで設定された、指定された休暇管理者のみが割当申請を承認する"
"必要があります。このオプションはデフォルトで選択されています。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:120
msgid ""
":guilabel:`By Employee's Approver`: Only the employee's specified approver "
"for time off, which is set on the *Work Information* tab on "
"the :ref:`employee's form <employees/work-info-tab>`, is required to approve "
"the allocation request."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`従業員の承認者による`: :ref:`従業員のフォーム <employees/work-"
"info-tab>`\\ の\\ *勤務情報*\\ タブで設定された、従業員の指定された休暇承認者"
"のみが、割り当て申請を承認する必要があります。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:123
msgid ""
":guilabel:`By Employee's Approver and Time Off Officer`: Both the "
"employee's :ref:`specified time off approver <employees/work-info-tab>` and "
"the time off officer are required to approve the allocation request."
msgstr ""
"\\ :guilabel:`従業員の承認者と休暇管理者による承認`\\ ：従業員の\\ :ref:`指定"
"された休暇承認者 <employees/work-info-tab>`\\ と休暇管理者の両方が割当申請を"
"承認する必要があります。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:None
msgid "The allocation section all filled out for  a new time off type."
msgstr "新しい休暇タイプのすべての割当セクションが入力されています。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:133
msgid ""
"This section determines all other details regarding the time off type, aside "
"from approvals and allocations."
msgstr ""
"このセクションでは、承認と割当以外の休暇タイプに関するその他すべての詳細を決"
"定します。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:136
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Ignore Public Holidays`: Enable this option if public holidays "
"should *not* be included in time off requests."
msgstr ""
"\\ :guilabel:`祝日を無視`\\ ：祝日を休暇申請に含めない場合は、このオプション"
"を有効にします。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:140
msgid ""
"An employee in the United States requests time off for the week of July 4th, "
"for a total of five days. Since the 4th of July is a holiday in the United "
"States, the time off request is automatically modified to use four vacation "
"days and one public holiday, instead of five vacation days. That is because "
"the holiday is ignored, and the user does not need to use their own vacation "
"time for a public holiday."
msgstr ""
"米国の従業員が7月4日の週に休暇を申請し、合計5日間を要求します。7月4日は米国の"
"祝日であるため、休暇申請は自動的に修正され、5日間の休暇ではなく、4日間の休暇"
"と1日の祝日を使用します。これは、祝日が無視され、ユーザーが祝日のために自分の"
"休暇を使用する必要がないためです。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:146
msgid ""
"This option reduces extra work for users, enabling them to make only one "
"time off request for the entire week, instead of making two separate "
"requests, one for the days *before* the holiday, and another one for the "
"days *after* the holiday."
msgstr ""
"このオプションにより、ユーザーの作業負担が軽減され、休日の\\ *前*\\ の日数"
"と\\ *後*\\ の日数で2つの別々の申請を行う代わりに、週全体に対して1つの休暇申"
"請のみを行うことができます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:150
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Hide On Dashboard`: Enable this option if this type of time off "
"should *not* appear on the dashboard."
msgstr ""
"\\ :guilabel:`ダッシュボードで非表示`\\ ：この種類の休暇をダッシュボードに表"
"示しない場合は、このオプションを有効にします。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:152
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Require Supporting Document`: Enable this option if the employee "
"**must** attach documents to the time off request. This is useful in "
"situations where documentation is required, such as long-term medical leave "
"or jury duty."
msgstr ""
"\\ :guilabel:`補足ドキュメントが必要`\\ ：従業員が休暇申請にドキュメントを添"
"付する必要がある場合は、このオプションを有効にします。これは、長期医療休暇や"
"陪審員の義務など、ドキュメントが必要な状況で役立ちます。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:155
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Deduct Extra Hours`: Enable this option if the time off request "
"should factor in any extra time accrued by the employee."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`追加勤務時間を控除`: 休暇申請で従業員が蓄積した追加時間を考慮する"
"必要がある場合は、このオプションを有効にします。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:159
msgid ""
"If an employee works two extra hours for the week, and requests five hours "
"of time off, the two extra worked hours are counted toward the request. As a "
"result, the time off request only uses three hours of the employee's accrual."
msgstr ""
"従業員が週に2時間の追加勤務を行い、5時間の休暇を申請した場合、追加で働いた2時"
"間が申請にカウントされます。その結果、休暇申請は従業員の積立時間のうち3時間の"
"みを使用します。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:163
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Eligible for Accrual Rate`: Enable this checkbox if the time off "
"type is included when calculating worked time for an accrual plan. This is "
"enabled by default."
msgstr ""
"\\ :guilabel:`積立率の対象`\\ ：積立プランの実勤務時間を計算する際に休暇"
"タイプを含める場合は、このチェックボックスを有効にします。これはデフォルトで"
"有効になっています。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:165
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Allow Request on Top`: Enable this checkbox if the employee can "
"request additional time off, stacked on top of this time off type."
msgstr ""
"\\ :guilabel:`上乗せ申請を許可`\\ ：従業員がこの休暇タイプの上に重ねて追加の"
"休暇を申請できる場合は、このチェックボックスを有効にします。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:169
msgid "Negative cap section"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:171
msgid ""
"Enable the :guilabel:`Allow Negative Cap` option if employees should be able "
"to request more time off than they currently have, allowing a negative "
"balance. If enabled, an :guilabel:`up to` field appears. In this field, "
"enter the maximum amount of negative time allowed, in days."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:176
msgid ""
"Sara currently has three days of the `Vacation` time off type. She is "
"planning a trip that requires five days of time off."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:179
msgid ""
